%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ukraine%20would%20be%20doing%20worse%20against%20Russia%20if%20it%20fought%20like%20Americans%20do%2C%20US%20veteran%20in%20Ukraine%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221895%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ukrainian%20soldiers%20stand%20next%20to%20the%20Leopard%201A5%20main%20battle%20tank%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650afe9cbf943d00195c5bd4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22947%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkrainian%20soldiers%20stand%20next%20to%20the%20Leopard%201A5%20main%20battle%20tank%20in%20Klietz%2C%20Germany%20August%2017%2C%202023%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FAnnegret%20Hilse%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EUkrainian%20soldiers%20would%20%26quot%3Bhave%20a%20bad%20time%26quot%3B%20if%20they%20used%20American%20fighting%20doctrine%20against%20Russia.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EHe%20added%20that%20Ukraine%20is%20ahead%20of%20the%20US%20in%20using%20drones%20as%20part%20of%20its%20military%20operations.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20that%20NATO%20training%20for%20Ukraine's%20troops%20includes%20discipline%2C%20which%20is%20unnecessary%20given%20the%20stakes.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20forces%20would%20be%20worse%20off%20if%20they%20followed%20American%20battlefield%20doctrine%20and%20are%20actually%20better%20at%20understanding%20some%20types%20of%20modern%20fighting%2C%20a%20US%20Army%20veteran%20who%20is%20training%20Ukrainian%20soldiers%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20use%20American%20doctrine%20here%2C%20we%20would%20definitely%20have%20a%20bad%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20trainer%2C%20who%20goes%20by%20the%20call%20sign%20Jackie%2C%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJackie%20fought%20in%20Afghanistan%20and%20Iraq%20before%20working%20as%20a%20training%20contractor%20for%20the%20US%20military%2C%20and%20has%20since%20gone%20to%20Ukraine%20to%20help%20train%20its%20troops%20and%20to%20fight%20alongside%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Ukraine's%20military%20is%20ahead%20of%20the%20US%20in%20some%20obvious%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20even%20have%20a%20clear%20doctrine%20for%20small%20drone%20use%20really%20at%20this%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20the%20US%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20Ukrainians%20are%20quite%20advanced%20in%20that%20fact.%20The%20Ukrainians%20are%20quite%20ahead%20of%20us%20on%20integration%20of%20these%20small%20drone%20systems%20and%20small%20medium%20drones.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20Ukraine%20has%20to%20operate%20in%20%26quot%3Bguerilla%20stealth%20mode%26quot%3B%20even%20when%20doing%20big%20operations%20because%20its%20forces%20are%20so%20disadvantaged%20as%20to%20be%20considered%20%26quot%3Binsufficient%20by%20any%20NATO%20country%20standard%20to%20breach%20the%20forces%20on%20that%20part%20of%20the%20line.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20has%20repeatedly%20thanked%20its%20Western%20partners%20for%20support%20and%20training%2C%20saying%20it%20has%20helped%20its%20troops.%20But%20some%20on%20the%20ground%20say%20they%20have%20to%20adjust%20that%20training%20to%20survive%20and%20win%20on%20the%20battlefield.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJackie's%20comments%20mirror%20those%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-officer-says-sticking-nato-training-would-get-killed-2023-9%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%3Emade%20in%20September%20by%20a%20Ukrainian%20commander%3C%2Fa%3E%20trained%20by%20US%2C%20British%2C%20and%20Polish%20soldiers%2C%20who%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20only%20did%20what%20%5BWestern%20militaries%5D%20taught%20me%2C%20I'd%20be%20dead.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20looks%20very%20different%20to%20those%20fought%20by%20Western%20countries%20over%20the%20past%20few%20decades%2C%20including%20conflicts%20like%20Afghanistan%20and%20Iraq%20where%20Western%20troops%20had%20significant%20equipment%20and%20weapons%20advantages%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-officer-says-sticking-nato-training-would-get-killed-2023-9%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%3EInsider%20previously%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20former%20Army%20Ranger%20who%20fought%20in%20Ukraine%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-army-ranger-ukraine-fighting-far-worse-than-afghanistan-iraq-2023-7%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%3Esaid%20the%20fighting%20there%20is%20worse%20than%20what%20he%20experienced%20in%20Iraq%20and%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20Ukrainians%20are%20getting%20trained%20by%20the%20country's%20allies%2C%20including%20the%20US%20training%20troops%20in%20Europe%2C%20Jackie%20said%20that%20training%20Ukrainian%20soldiers%20%26quot%3Bfrom%20the%20ground%20up%26quot%3B%20is%20not%20appropriate%20given%20how%20much%20the%20soldiers%20have%20already%20fought%2C%20and%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20fight%20they%20have%20left%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20some%20of%20the%20soldiers%20he%20works%20with%20returned%20from%20NATO%20training%20and%20told%20him%20they%20were%20standing%20in%20formation%20for%20two%20hours%20%26quot%3Bso%20they%20could%20learn%20discipline%20and%20leadership.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGuys%2C%20their%20people%20are%20dying%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20need%20to%20convince%20them%20to%20stand%20for%20two%20hours%20in%20formation%20to%20learn%20what%20discipline%20means.%20Their%20relatives'%20blood%20is%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20so%20teach%20them%20how%20to%20fight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJackie%20also%20pushed%20back%20against%20the%20idea%20that%20Ukraine%20should%20rigidly%20follow%20NATO%20standard%20training%2C%20and%20even%20argued%20that%20such%20a%20thing%20doesn't%20really%20exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20keep%20hearing%20'NATO%20standard'%20getting%20thrown%20around%2C%20and%20'NATO%20standard%20training'%20or%20'NATO%20standard%20doctrine'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20Polish%20infantry%20does%20not%20fight%20the%20same%20way%20as%20the%20American%20infantry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20those%20training%20Ukrainians%2C%20he%20said%2C%20simply%3A%20%26quot%3BDon't%20get%20worked%20up%20about%20the%20procedures%20and%20the%20organizational%20stuff%20and%20ribbons%20and%20medals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20look%20at%20Ukraine's%20progress%2C%20and%20see%20if%20they%20have%20any%20specific%20training%20or%20equipment%20that%20could%20help.%20%26quot%3BGet%20them%20something%20they%20can%20use%20and%20the%20thing%20you%20teach%20them%20to%20do%2C%20they're%20going%20to%20do%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-shouldnt-follow-us-military-doctrine-warfare-better-trainer-russia-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695722122000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650afe9cbf943d00195c5bd4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-shouldnt-follow-us-military-doctrine-warfare-better-trainer-russia-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ukrainian%20soldiers%20have%20to%20fight%20Russia%20differently%20from%20the%20way%20US%20soldiers%20would%20be%20made%20to%20do%20it%2C%20a%20US%20veteran%20in%20Ukraine%20told%20Insider.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sbaker%40insider.com%20(Sin%C3%A9ad%20Baker)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-shouldnt-follow-us-military-doctrine-warfare-better-trainer-russia-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%228%20Injured%20After%20JetBlue%20Flight%20Caught%20In%20%26quot%3BSevere%20Turbulence%26quot%3B%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEight%20passengers%20of%20a%20JetBlue%20flight%20from%20Ecuador%20to%20Fort%20Lauderdale%20in%20Florida%20were%20hospitalised%