3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3ECauvery%20Water-Sharing%20History%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20battle%20that%20has%20raged%20for%20over%20a%20century%20should%20have%20concluded%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%202018%20order%2C%20which%20specified%20how%20much%20each%20party%20(including%20the%20city%20of%20Bengaluru%2C%20Kerala%20and%20Puducherry)%20should%20get%20from%20the%20Cauvery.%20The%20court's%20order%20was%20a%20revision%20of%20the%202007%20order%20passed%20by%20a%20tribunal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20never%20been%20that%20simple%20though%2C%20with%20Karnataka%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20frequently%20accusing%20the%20other%20of%20demanding%20too%20much%20and%20sharing%20too%20little%2C%20respectively.%20One%20problem%20is%20lack%20of%20clarity%20over%20water-sharing%20in%20a%20'distress%20year'%2C%20or%20a%20year%20in%20which%20there%20has%20been%20less-than-normal%20rainfall.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20dispute%20dates%20back%20to%20the%20colonial%20period.%20In%20a%201924%20agreement%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Puducherry%20were%20to%20get%20the%20lion's%20share%20of%20surplus%20water%20from%20the%20to-be-built%20Krishna%20Raja%20Sagar%20dam.%20Less%20than%20three%20decades%20later%20there%20was%20trouble%20again%2C%20including%20violent%20clashes%20over%20the%20construction%20of%20more%20dams.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20possibly%20when%20the%20water-sharing%20dispute%20really%20took%20off%2C%20as%20Tamil%20Nadu%20is%20a%20lower%20riparian%20state%20and%20was%2C%20by%20then%2C%20dependent%20on%20water%20from%20the%20Cauvery%20to%20water%20its%20crops.%20A%20proposal%20for%20Karnataka%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20to%20each%20share%2047%20per%20cent%20of%20total%20water%20was%20refused%20by%20the%20latter%20state%20and%2C%20in%201986%2C%20the%20matter%20reached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20ordered%20a%20tribunal%20to%20settle%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Brea