ial%20comment%20on%20the%20matter%20is%20still%20awaited.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20China%2C%20Shiyan%206%20(Experiment%206)%20is%20out%20on%20an%20%E2%80%9Cexpeditionary%20voyage%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20eastern%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%2C%20after%20it%20had%20left%20Guangzhou%2C%20south%20China%E2%80%99s%20Guangdong%20Province.%20%E2%80%9COrganised%20by%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%20Institute%20of%20Oceanology%20(SCSIO)%20under%20the%20Chinese%20Academy%20of%20Sciences%2C%20the%20vessel%20is%20scheduled%20to%20operate%20at%20sea%20for%2080%20days%20with%2028%20scientific%20research%20projects%20from%2013%20research%20teams%20onboard%2C%20covering%20a%20range%20of%20more%20than%2012%2C000%20nautical%20miles%20(roughly%2022%2C200%20km)%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20report%20from%20China%E2%80%99s%20state-run%20news%20channel%20CGTN%20had%20said%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChinese%20%E2%80%9Cresearch%20ships%E2%80%9D%20are%20said%20to%20usually%20have%20%E2%80%9Cdual%20purposes%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Flanka-clears-docking-of-chinese-research-ship-545633%5C%22%3Esays%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Tribune%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20while%20the%20primary%20aim%20is%20scientific%20exploration%2C%20what%20raises%20the%20hackles%20of%20other%20countries%20is%20the%20geopolitical%20purposes%20for%20which%20they%20are%20also%20deployed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20said%20that%20the%20National%20Aquatic%20Resources%20Research%20and%20Development%20Agency%20(NARA)%20of%20Sri%20Lanka%20is%20a%20partner%20in%20the%20Chinese%20vessel%E2%80%99s%20research%20activities%20in%20Sri%20Lankan%20waters%2C%20and%20the%20research%20collected%20in%20the%20process%20would%20be%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%E2%80%99s%20possession.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20concern%20over%20the%20visit%20of%20the%20Chinese%20vessel%20is%20due%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20comes%20months%20after%20a%20Chinese%20warship%20was%20docked%20at%