am's%20travel%20to%20Hyderabad.%20The%20visa%20clearance%20came%20less%20than%2048%20hours%20before%20Pakistan's%20scheduled%20travel%20to%20India%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20September%2027.%20They%20play%20their%20first%20warm-up%20game%20against%20New%20Zealand%20in%20Hyderabad%20on%20September%2029.%20%26quot%3BVisas%20have%20been%20issued%20to%20Pakistan%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20ICC%20spokesperson%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20confusion%20remained%20in%20the%20Pakistan%20camp%20over%20the%20grant%20of%20visa.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20not%20got%20the%20call%20from%20Indian%20High%20Commission%20yet%20over%20visa%20clearance.%20Member%20of%20our%20team%20is%20stationed%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20PCB%20spokesperon%20Umar%20Farooq%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20confirmation%20from%20the%20ICC%20came%20after%20the%20PCB%20wrote%20to%20ICC%20CEO%20Geoff%20Allardice%20on%20Monday%20over%20the%20visa%20delay%20besides%20claiming%20the%20anxious%20wait%20has%20adversely%20impacted%20the%20team's%20preparation%20for%20the%2050-over%20showpiece.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPakistan%20were%20supposed%20to%20have%20a%20two-day%20team%20bonding%20session%20in%20Dubai%20before%20their%20scheduled%20arrival%20in%20Hyderabad%20on%20September%2027%20but%20was%20cancelled%20due%20to%20the%20uncertainty%20over%20Indian%20visa.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Babar%20Azam-led%20side%20plays%20two%20warm-up%20games%20and%20as%20many%20World%20Cup%20matches%20in%20Hyderabad%20starting%20with%20the%20practice%20fixture%20against%20New%20Zealand.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E(With%20PTI%20Inputs)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695716820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fvkfmhd2o_babar-azam-806_625x300_26_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fbabar-azam-reprimanded-over-traffic-violation-says-report-handed-fine-of-4424364%22%2C%22summar