0post%20to%20pay%20her%20heartfelt%20tribute%20to%20the%20legendary%20star.%20She%20has%20shared%20two%20throwback%20pictures.%20While%20the%20first%20frame%20was%20a%20still%20from%20the%20film%3Cem%3E%20Hare%20Rama%20Hare%20Krishna%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20second%20photo%20is%20from%20%3Cem%3EHeera%20Panna%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20released%20in%201973.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Zeenat%20Aman%2C%20Dev%20Anand%20was%20%26quot%3Bstylish%2C%20suave%2C%20prolific%2C%20a%20dynamo%20beyond%20compare%2C%20and%20generosity%20of%20talent%26quot%3B.%20She%20added%2C%C2%A0%26quot%3BHe%C2%A0%20%5BDev%20Anand%5D%20sparked%20careers%20(mine%20included)%2C%20brought%20together%20creative%20heads%2C%20and%20made%20films%20that%20resonated%20across%20generations.%C2%A0It%20gladdens%20my%20heart%20to%20see%20his%20legacy%20honoured%20an%20entire%20century%20since%20his%20birth.%20In%20recent%20days%2C%20I've%20been%20overwhelmed%20with%20requests%20for%20comments%20about%20him%20but%20there%20is%20little%20to%20add%20to%20what%20I've%20already%20said.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EZeena%20Aman%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20three-part%20Instagram%20series%20that%20she%20shared%20earlier%20in%20April%20this%20year.%20She%20said%2C%C2%A0%26quot%3BThough%20I%20posted%20a%20three-part%20series%20about%20him%20just%20a%20few%20weeks%20ago%2C%20I%20can't%20resist%20the%20nostalgia%20of%20these%20two%20frames%20from%20our%20earliest%20films%20together.%20They%20will%20be%20instantly%20recognisable%20to%20my%20older%20followers%2C%20but%20I%20am%20not%20so%20sure%20about%20you%20younger%20lot.%26quot%3B%20Reacting%20to%20the%20post%2C%20Sanjay%20Kapoor%20commented%3A%20%26quot%3BIconic%20film...iconic%20picture.%26quot%3B%C2%A0Chitrangda%20Singh%20dropped%20a%20series%20of%20heart-eye%20emojis%20in%20the%20comments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%