omeone%20who%20sees%20the%20glimmer%20of%20potential%20and%20ambition%20that%20has%20perhaps%20only%20been%20visible%20to%20the%20self%20thus%20far.%20Very%20few%20are%20so%20lucky%20as%20to%20find%20this%20person%2C%20but%20I%20was.%20My%20starmaker%20was%20Dev%20%5BAnand%5D%20saab.%26quot%3B%20Zeenat%20Aman%20revealed%20that%20when%20she%20and%20her%20family%20were%20packing%20bags%20to%20leave%20India%2C%20it%20was%20Dev%20Anand%20who%20persuaded%20her%20%5BZeenat%20Aman%5D%20mother%20to%20delay%20their%20relocation%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%201970%2C%20and%20I%20think%20O%20P%20Ralhan%20was%20feeling%20quite%20sorry%20for%20me.%20He%20had%20given%20me%20a%20bit%20part%20in%20%3Ci%3EHulchul%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20it%20had%20made%20little%20impact%2C%20and%20I%20was%20already%20packing%20my%20bags%20to%20relocate%20to%20Malta%20with%20my%20mother%20and%20stepfather.%20Dev%20Saab%20and%20his%20Navketan%20team%20were%20casting%20for%20%3Ci%3EHare%20Rama%20Hare%20Krishna%20%3C%2Fi%3Eat%20the%20time.%20In%20his%20largesse%2C%20O%20P%20Ralhan%20suggested%20that%20they%20meet%20me.%20I%20vividly%20remember%20what%20I%20wore%20that%20day.%20A%20fitted%20yellow%20top%2C%20a%20fawn-coloured%20skirt%20and%20glasses%20with%20yellow%20frames.%20My%20mother%20was%20at%20the%20meeting%20(remember%2C%20I%20was%20still%20in%20my%20teens).%20So%20she%20held%20forth%2C%20while%20I%20spoke%20when%20spoken%20to%2C%20and%20packed%20tobacco%20into%20my%20pipe.%20The%20meeting%20concluded%2C%20and%20a%20few%20days%20later%20the%20landline%20jangled.%20I%20was%20asked%20to%20come%20for%20a%20screen%20test%2C%20and%20that%20is%20how%20I%20came%20to%20be%20cast%20as%20Jasbir%2FJanice.%20Oh%2C%20but%20the%20saga%20doesn't%20end%20here.%20My%20family%20was%20ready%20to%20depart%20the%20country%2C%20but%20Dev%20%5BAnand%5D%20saab%20persuaded%20my%20mother%20and%20I%20to%20delay%20our%20travels.%20So%20instead%20we%20flew%20to%20Kathmandu%2C%20stayed%20at%20the%20famous%20Soaltee%20Hotel%2C%20and%20waited%20long%20days%20to%20be%20called%20to%20set%20to%20shoot!%20I%20was%20frothing%20at%20the%20bit%20by%20the%20time%20it%20was%20finally%20time%20for%20my%20scenes.%20The%20first%20of%20which%20was%20a%20bus%20sequence.%20It%20makes%20me%20laugh%20to%20watch%20it%20now%20because%20I%20know%20I'm%20practically%20spitting%20out%20my%20lines%20in%20my%20impatience%20to%20prove%20myself!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EHare%20Rama%20Hare%20Krishna%20%3C%2Fi%3Ewas%20a%20%E2%80%9Chuge%20hit%E2%80%9D%20and%20Zeenat%20Aman%20became%20an%20overnight%20sensation.%20Following%20the%20success%20of%20the%20film%2C%20Zeenat%20Aman's%20immigration%20plans%20were%20postponed%20for%20an%20indefinite%20period.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20those%20days%20it%20took%20much%20longer%20to%20make%20a%20film%20from%20start%20to%20finish.%20Two%20or%20three%20years%20even.%20My%20mother%20and%20I%20once%20again%20prepared%20to%20leave%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20yet%20again%20Dev%20Saab%20persuaded%20us%20to%20stay.%20He%20promised%20to%20edit%20quickly%20and%20get%20the%20movie%20into%20the%20cinemas.%20Sure%20enough%2C%20the%20film%20was%20released%2C%20it%20became%20a%20huge%20hit%2C%20and%20I%20became%20a%20star.%20My%20immigration%20plans%20were%20now%20indefinitely%20postponed%2C%20and%20Dev%20Saab%20started%20writing%20another%20script%20with%20me%20in%20mind%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20finished%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCrdY-DXtESa%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCrdY-DXtESa%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_camp