khee's%20sister)%20Panna%20in%20%3Ci%3EHeera%20Panna%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20which%20was%20released%20in%201973.%20I%20had%20a%20blast%20shooting%20that%20film%2C%20and%20its%20soundtrack%20remains%20a%20favourite%20to%20this%20day.%20Dev%20%5BAnand%5D%20saab%20was%20a%20dynamic%20mentor.%20Our%20association%20continued%2C%20and%20next%20on%20the%20cards%20was%20I%3Ci%3Eshk%20Ishk%20Ishk%3C%2Fi%3E.%20I%20once%20again%20found%20myself%20in%20Nepal%2C%20but%20this%20time%20we%20were%20shooting%20in%20the%20picturesque%20lake%20town%20of%20Pokhara!%20Those%20of%20you%20who%20have%20seen%20the%20film%20know%20that%20it%20features%20a%20bevy%20of%20lovely%20women%20as%20my%20sisters%20and%20friends.%20They%20were%20literally%20so%2C%20because%20prior%20to%20the%20shoot%20Dev%20%5BAnand%5D%20saab%20asked%20if%20I%20had%20any%20%E2%80%9Cmodel%20friends%E2%80%9D%20who%20could%20join%20the%20project.%20I%20put%20the%20word%20out%2C%20several%20friends%20answered%20my%20call%2C%20and%20so%20it%20was%20quite%20the%20party%20in%20Pokhara.%20With%20a%20good-looking%20and%20young%20cast%20and%20crew%2C%20it%20should%20be%20no%20surprise%20that%20there%20were%20plenty%20of%20dalliances%20and%20heartbreaks%20unfolding%20behind%20the%20scenes.%20But%20please%20don't%20expect%20the%20gossipy%20details%20from%20me!%20Would%20you%20like%20the%20world%20to%20know%20about%20your%20every%20crush%2C%20humiliation%20or%20affair%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20her%20experience%20of%20working%20with%20Dev%20Anand%2C%20Zeenat%20Aman%20said%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cseamless%20and%20joyful%E2%80%9D%20as%20the%20superstar%20was%20%E2%80%9Ca%20fount%20of%20creative%20energy.%E2%80%9D%20While%20Zeenat%20Aman's%20career%20was%20blooming%20and%20fresh%20offers%20were%20pouring%2C%20one%20of%20these%20led%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfirst%20and%20the%20only%20misunderstanding%E2%80%9D%20between%20her%20and%20Dev%20Anand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnyway%2C%20Dev%20%5BAnand%5D%20saab%20was%20on%20a%20roll.%20Working%20with%20him%20was%20seamless%20and%20joyful.%20He%20was%20a%20fount%20of%20creative%20energy%2C%20and%20I%20was%20delighted%20to%20have%20his%20guidance.%20It%20would%20have%20been%20easy%20for%20him%20to%20tie%20me%20down%20to%20a%20contract%2C%20but%20he%20had%20the%20grace%20to%20never%20even%20suggest%20it.%20Thus%20allowing%20me%20a%20chance%20to%20spread%20my%20wings.%20We%20also%20starred%20together%20in%20several%20films%20made%20by%20other%20directors%20such%20as%20Darling%2C%20Darling%20and%20Kalabaaz.%20My%20career%20was%20booming%2C%20fresh%20offers%20were%20pouring%20in%2C%20but%20alas%2C%20one%20of%20these%2C%20led%20to%20the%20first%20and%20only%20misunderstanding%20between%20Dev%20%5BAnand%5D%20saab%20and%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20quipped.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCrf7iaStftt%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCrf7iaStftt%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCrf7iaStftt%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%