won't%20repeat%20it.%20I%20was%20giddy%20to%20have%20been%20cast%20for%20Raj%20%5BKapoor%5D%20ji's%20unconventional%20project%2C%20and%20put%20heart%20and%20soul%20into%20it.%20I%20was%20completely%20unaware%20that%20Dev%20%5BAnand%5D%20saab%20was%20simultaneously%20misreading%20the%20situation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EZeenat%20Aman%20continued%2C%20%E2%80%9CYears%20later%2C%20in%202007%2C%20%E2%80%98Romancing%20with%20Life'%2C%20Dev%20%5BAnand%5D%20Saab's%20autobiography%20hit%20the%20stands.%20In%20it%2C%20he%20professed%20that%20he%20was%20in%20love%20with%20me%2C%20and%20insinuated%20that%20Raj%20%5BKapoor%5D%20ji%20and%20I%20had%20more%20than%20a%20director-actor%20equation%20which%20broke%20his%20heart.%20To%20be%20honest%2C%20I%20was%20livid.%20I%20felt%20humiliated%2C%20hurt%20and%20disconcerted%20that%20Dev%20%5BAnand%5D%20saab%2C%20my%20much%20older%20mentor%2C%20a%20person%20I%20loved%20and%20admired%20platonically%2C%20would%20not%20only%20believe%20such%20a%20story%20devoid%20of%20a%20shred%20of%20truth%20but%20would%20then%20go%20on%20to%20publish%20it%20for%20the%20world%20to%20read.%20For%20weeks%20my%20phone%20rang%20incessantly%20as%20friends%20inquired%20about%20%E2%80%9Cwhat%20happened%E2%80%9D%20and%20shared%20excerpts%20from%20the%20book.%20I%20never%20did%20read%20it%20though%2C%20and%20in%20my%20anger%2C%20I%20consigned%20the%20copy%20I%20was%20sent%20to%20storage%20in%20the%20basement!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20great%20misunderstanding%E2%80%9D%20which%20embarrassed%20Zeenat%20Aman%20deeply%2C%20the%20actress%20stated%20that%20she%20will%20always%20remember%20Dev%20Anand%20for%20%E2%80%9Chis%20rare%20talent%20and%20warm%20guidance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCrlMeQwrUff%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3