g-to-pay-emis-4424373%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Waheeda%20Rehman%20To%20Receive%20Dadasaheb%20Phalke%20Award%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBollywood%20legend%20Waheeda%20Rehman%20will%20receive%20the%20Dadasaheb%20Phalke%20Award%20for%202021%2C%20announced%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%20Minister%20Anurag%20Thakur.%20Considered%20one%20of%20Indian%20cinema's%20most%20talented%20and%20elegant%20actors%2C%20Waheeda%20Rehman%2C%2085%2C%20is%20beloved%20for%20her%20work%20in%20films%20like%20%3Cem%3EGuide%2C%20Pyaasa%2C%20Kaagaz%20Ke%20Phool%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EChaudhvin%20Ka%20Chaand%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Her%20accolades%20include%20the%20Padma%20Bhushan%20and%20Padma%20Shri.%20The%20Dadasaheb%20Phalke%20Award%20is%20the%20country's%20highest%20film%20honour%20and%20is%20given%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Anurag%20Thakur%20wrote%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%20an%20immense%20sense%20of%20happiness%20and%20honour%20in%20announcing%20that%20Waheeda%20Rehman%20ji%20is%20being%20bestowed%20with%20the%20prestigious%20Dadasaheb%20Phalke%20Lifetime%20Achievement%20Award%20this%20year%20for%20her%20stellar%20contribution%20to%20Indian%20Cinema.%20Waheeda%20ji%20has%20been%20critically%20acclaimed%20for%20her%20roles%20in%20Hindi%20films%2C%20prominent%20among%20them%2C%20%3Cem%3EPyaasa%2C%20Kaagaz%20ke%20Phool%2C%20Chaudhavi%20Ka%20Chand%2C%20Saheb%20Biwi%20Aur%20Ghulam%2C%20Guide%2C%20Khamoshi%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20several%20others.%20In%20her%20career%20spanning%20over%205%20decades%2C%20she%20has%20essayed%20her%20roles%20with%20extreme%20finesse%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20National%20Film%20Award%20for%20her%20role%20as%20a%20clanswoman%20in%20the%20film%20%3Cem%3EReshma%20Aur%20Shera%3C%2Fem%3E.%20A%20Padma%20Shri%20and%20Padma%20Bhushan%20awardee%2C%20Waheeda%20ji%20has%20exemplified%20dedication%2C%20commitment%20and%20the%20strength%20of%20a%20Bharatiya%20Nari%20who%20can%20achieve%20the%20highest%20level%20of%20professional%20excellence%20with%20her%20hardwork.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20a%20time%20when%20the%20historic%20Nari%20Shakti%20Vandan%20Adhiniyam%20has%20been%20passed%20by%20Parliament%2C%20her%20being%20awarded%20with%20this%20lifetime%20achievement%20award%20is%20a%20fitting%20tribute%20to%20one%20of%20the%20leading%20ladies%20of%20Indian%20Cinema%20and%20one%20who%20has%20dedicated%20her%20life%20after%20films%20to%20philanthropy%20and%20the%20greater%20good%20of%20society.%20I%20congratulate%20her%20and%20humbly%20pay%20my%20regards%20to%20her%20rich%20body%20of%20work%20that%20is%20an%20intrinsic%20part%20of%20our%20film%20history.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERead%20his%20post%20here%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EI%20feel%20an%20immense%20sense%20of%20happiness%20and%20honour%20in%20announcing%20that%20Waheeda%20Rehman%20ji%20is%20being%20bestowed%20with%20the%20prestigious%20Dadasaheb%20Phalke%20Lifetime%20Achievement%20Award%20this%20year%20for%20her%20stellar%20contribution%20to%20Indian%20Cinema.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20Waheeda%20ji%20has%20been%20critically%20acclaimed%20for%20her%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Anurag%20Thakur%20(%40ianuragthakur)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fianuragthakur%2Fstatus%2F1706565710540083673%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2026%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Dadasaheb%20Phalke%20Award%20announcement%20coincides%20with%20late%20actor%20Dev%20Anand's%20centenary%20-%20Dev%20Anand%20was%20Waheeda%20Rehman's%20co-star%20in%20one%20of%20her%20most%20seminal%20films%2C%201965's%20%3Cem%3EGuide%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Dev%20Anand%2C%20who%20received%20the%20Dadasaheb%20Phalke%20Award%20in%202002%2C%20would%20have%20been%20100%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWaheeda%20Rehman%20will%20receive%20the%20award%20in%20a%20ceremony%20later%20this%20year.%20The%20previous%20winner%20of%20the%20Dadasaheb%20