p%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20Sardar%20Sarovar%20Project%20(SSP)%20on%20the%20Narmada%20River%20overflowed%2C%20flooding%20downstream%20districts%20of%20Bharuch%2C%20Narmada%2C%20Vadodara%2C%20Panchmahal%2C%20and%20Dahod.%20There%20have%20been%20allegations%20that%20the%20flood%20was%20actually%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fgujarat-govt-under-fire-for-holding-back-narmada-waters-for-pm-modis-birthday-causing-floods%5C%22%3Eman-made%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20disaster%20as%20the%20authorities%20had%20withheld%20waters%20in%20the%20dam%20for%20two%20days%20before%20releasing%20a%20huge%20volume%20(18%20lakh%20cusecs)%20all%20at%20once%20on%20September%2017%20to%20%E2%80%9Cplease%E2%80%9D%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20who%20celebrated%20his%2073rd%20birthday%20that%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fgujarat-govt-under-fire-for-holding-back-narmada-waters-for-pm-modis-birthday-causing-floods%5C%22%3EGujarat%20Govt%20Under%20Fire%20for%20%E2%80%98Holding%20Back%20Narmada%20Waters%20for%20PM%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Birthday%20Causing%20Floods%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20notification%20issued%20on%20September%2022%2C%20every%20affected%20family%20would%20a%20total%20of%20Rs%207%2C000%20in%20aid%20from%20the%20State%20Disaster%20Response%20Fund%20(SDRF)%3B%20Rs%202%2C500%20for%20clothing%20and%20Rs%202%2C500%20for%20household%20goods.%20The%20government%20said%20it%20has%20actually%20made%20a%20special%20provision%20to%20provide%20another%20Rs%202%2C000%20from%20the%20state%20budget%20to%20the%20affected%20families%2C%20totaling%20the%20amount%20of%20compensation%20to%20Rs%207%2C000%20per%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20today%E2%80%99s%20inflationary%20times%2C%20tell%20me%20what%20kind%20of%20household%20goods%20can%20be%20purchased%20for%202%2C500%20rupees%20for%20the%20entire%20family%2C%20what%20kind%20of%20clothing%20can%20be%20purchased%20for%202%2C500%20if%20there%20are%2010%20people%20in%20a%20family%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Fsep%2F25%2Fjoke-narmada-flood-victims-call-out-governmentsrelief-package-2618103.html%5C%22%3Equoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20Suresh%20Patel%20of%20Juna%20Borbhata%20village%20in%20south%20Gujarat%E2%80%99s%20Bharuch%20district.%20Bharuch%20district%20suffered%20the%20most%20due%20to%20the%20floods.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20many%20people%20will%20be%20able%20to%20dress%3F%20How%20many%20pairs%20of%20chappals%20would%20you%20need%20to%20buy%20for%20ten%20individuals%20if%20each%20pair%20cost%20100%20rupees%2C%20and%20would%20you%20be%20able%20to%20buy%20clothing%20for%20the%20remaining%20family%20members%3F%E2%80%9D%20Suresh%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20notification%20also%20offered%20Rs%2020%2C000%20from%20SDRF%20to%20those%20whose%20houses%20have%20been%20completely%20demolished%20or%20have%20suffered%20serious%20damage.%20An%20additional%20Rs%2010%2C000%20would%20be%20given%20to%20partially%20damaged%20residential%20kutcha%2Fpucca%20dwellings%20that%20have%20suffered%20at%20least%2015%25%20damage%2C%20and%20Rs%2010%2C000%20for%20entirely%20destroyed%20or%20partially%20damaged%20shacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVictims%20say%20the%20compensation%20is%20extremely%20inadequate.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20caused%20the%20wound%20and%20is%20now%20attempting%20to%20offer%20ointment.%20The%20government%20claims%20that%20if%20the%20entire%20building%20is%20demolished%2C%20they%20will%20receive%20Rs%201%2C20%2C000%20in%20aid.%20Ask%20the%20government%20how%20the%20house%20will%20be%20constructed%20with%20this%20amount%20of%20money.%20Are%20cement%2C%20brick%2C%20and%20concrete%20pricing%20unknown%20to%20the%20government%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Dalpat%20Patel%20of%20Juna%20Borbhatha%20village.%20%E2%80%9CWho%20will%20build%20a%20shed%20for%205%2C000%20rupees%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20inflationary%20time%2C%20as%20claimed%20by%20the%20government%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20farmers%20have%20expressed%20disappointment%20over%20the%20compensation%20and%20norms%20announced%20by%20the%20government%20for%20hectares%20of%20standing%20crops%20that%20they%20had%20lost.%20The%20government%20notification%20said%20only%20those%20who%20had%20suffered%2033%25%20or%20more%20to%20their%20standing%20crops%20would%20be%20eligible%20for%20compensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAccording%20to%20the%20special%20relief%20package%2C%20farmers%20who%20have%20suffered%2033%25%20or%20more%20damage%20to%20non-irrigated%20kharif%20crops%20will%20receive%20a%20compensation%20of%20Rs%208%2C500%20per%20hectare%20up%20to%20a%20maximum%20of%202%20hectare%20while%20irrigated%20farms%20that%20sowed%20kharif%20crops%20will%20receive%20a%20compensation%20of%20Rs%2017%2C000%20per%20hectare%20and%20an%20additional%20compensation%20of%20Rs%208%2C000%20per%20hectare%20from%20the%20state%20treasury%2C%20in%20all%20providing%20Rs%2025%2C000%20per%20hectare%20for%20a%20maximum%20of%202%20hectares%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20notification%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGujarat%20Congress%20spokesperson%20Manish%20Doshi%20called%20compensation%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmockery%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CFarmers%20in%20Bharuch%2C%20Narmada%20and%20Vadodara%20districts%20have%20suffered%20huge%20losses%20due%20to%20this%20man-made%20disaster.%20Approximately%20four%20lakh%20farmers%20have%20suffered%20losses%20in%20the%20region%20and%20so%20the%20compensation%20package%20announced%20by%20the%20government%20is%20a%20mockery.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20Congress%20party%20had%20said%20floods%20could%20have%20been%20prevented%20if%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%20kept%20the%20safety%20of%20people%20in%20mind%20instead%20of%20trying%20to%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fgujarat-govt-under-fire-for-holding-back-narmada-waters-for-pm-modis-birthday-causing-floods%5C%22%3Eplease%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20Modi.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20this%20happened%20because%20September%2017%20was%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20birthday%2C%20and%20for%20that%20occasion%2C%20the%20dam%20was%20filled%2C%20and%20the%20chief%20minister%20went%20there%20to%20perform%20a%20pooja.%20To%20carry%20out%20this%20drama%2C%20the%20water%2C%20which%20had%20been%20rising%20since%20last%20week%2C%20was%20not%20released%2C%20and%20the%20turbines%20were%20shut%20down.%20Instead%2C%20if%20the%20water%20had%20been%20released%20in%20smaller%20installments%2C%20this%20destruction%20would%20not%20have%20occurred%2C%20and%20people%20would%20not%20have%20suffered%20so%20much%2C%E2%80%9D%20Congress%20state%20unit%20president%20Shaktisinh%20Gohil%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695714635000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19135716%2FThe-Wire-13.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fa-cruel-joke-flood-victims-slam-gujarat-govt-say-compensation-not-enough%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20SSP%20project%20on%20Narmada%20River%20overflowed%20flooding%20five%20districts%2C%20allegedly%20after%20authorities%20withheld%20water%20for%20two%20days%20before%20releasing%20it%20all%20at%20once%20on%20Narendra%20Modi's%20birthday%20on%20September%2017.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fa-cruel-joke-flood-victims-slam-gujarat-govt-say-compensation-not-enough%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CBDT%20extends%20safe%20harbour%20option%20to%20convertible%20preference%20shares%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695714279000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2018-12%2F23%2Ffull%2F1545587807-1186.jpg%22%2C%22originID