%20sensibilities%20of%20other%20fellow%20commuters.%20DMRC's%20Operations%20%26amp%3B%20Maintenance%20Act%20in%20fact%20lists%20out%20indecency%20as%20a%20punishable%20offence%20under%20Section%2059%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695711480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fers1mm5g_man-smoking-inside-delhi-metro_625x300_26_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-of-man-smoking-inside-train-coach-goes-viral-delhi-metro-reacts-4424337%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20Metro%20Rail%20Corporation%20(DMRC)%20has%20taken%20note%20of%20the%20same%20and%20said%20that%20it%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Bobjectionable%20behaviour%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-of-man-smoking-inside-train-coach-goes-viral-delhi-metro-reacts-4424337%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-of-man-smoking-inside-train-coach-goes-viral-delhi-metro-reacts-4424337%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-of-man-smoking-inside-train-coach-goes-viral-delhi-metro-reacts-4424337%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22For%20How%20Long%20Will%20We%20Ignore%20the%20Extrajudicial%20Killings%20on%20Indian%20Soil%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22095913%2FF6ga_ibawAAlDWp.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EExtra-judicial%20killings%20are%20normal%20in%20India%20and%20are%20called%20encounters.%20They%20refer%20to%20the%20State%E2%80%99s%20murder%20of%20an%20accused%20who%20is%20often%2C%20though%20not%20always%2C%20in%20custody.%20And%20this%20killing%20happens%20even%20if%20the%20accused%20has%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20protection%20with%20the%20specific%20plea%20that%20they%20are%20in%20danger.%20The%20killings%20happen%20even%20if%20the%20accused%20is%20being%20filmed%20while%20being%20transported%20from%20one%20location%20to%20another%2C%20and%20filmed%20because%20it%20is%20thought%20that%20they%20might%20be%20killed.%20The%20theory%20applied%20is%20that%20the%20justice%20system%20is%20broken%20and%20punishment%20cannot%20wait.%20That%20the%20world%20has%20good%20people%20and%20bad%20people%2C%20and%20the%20latter%20do%20not%20require%20to%20be%20convicted%20before%20being%20punished%20and%20this%20punishment%20can%20come%20from%20outside%20the%20legal%20system%20through%20shooting%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2027%2C%202013%2C%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20Gurudas%20Dasgupta%20asked%20the%20home%20ministry%20some%20questions.%20They%20included%20whether%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20commission%20headed%20by%20Justice%20N.%20Santosh%20Hegde%20appointed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20seven%20killings%20in%20six%20separate%20instances%20in%20Manipur%20were%20the%20consequence%20of%20fake%20encounters.%20And%20whether%20the%20National%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20has%20demanded%20an%20investigation%20into%20all%20encounters%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20replied%20that%20it%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20Hegde%20commission%2C%20but%20that%20the%20NHRC%20has%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20demanded%20any%20investigation%E2%80%9D%20into%20the%20findings%20and%20therefore%20the%20government%20had%20done%20nothing%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20instructive%20to%20go%20into%20what%20this%20commission%20is%20and%20what%20it%20did.%20On%20November%2024%2C%202012%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20set%20up%20a%20commission%20of%20three%20people%2C%20including%20former%20Justice%20Hegde%2C%20former%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20J.M.%20Lyngdoh%20and%20former%20DGP%20of%20Karnataka%20Ajay%20Kumar%20Singh.%20Their%20task%20was%20to%20take%20up%20the%20murders%20of%201%2C528%20people%20between%201979%20and%202012%20in%20Manipur%20through%20encounters.%20The%20murders%20were%20committed%20by%20the%20Manipur%20police%20and%20the%20security%20forces.%20The%20matter%20came%20up%20after%20the%20Extra%20Judicial%20Execution%20Victim%20Families%20Association%20(EEVFAM)%20filed%20a%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22UP%3A%20Four%20Times%20More%20People%20Killed%20in%20'Police%20Action'%20Under%20Adityanath%20Than%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fup-four-times-more-people-killed-in-police-action-under-adityanath-than-akhilesh-yadav%5C%22%3EUP%3A%20Four%20Times%20More%20People%20Killed%20in%20%E2%80%98Police%20Action%E2%80%99%20Under%20Adityanath%20Than%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20commission%20took%20up%20the%20first%20six%20of%20the%201%2C528%20murders%20and%20by%202013%20found%20that%20all%20of%20the%20encounters%20were%20fake.%20The%20murders%20were%20facilitated%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20killers%20were%20protected%20by%20AFSPA%2C%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20Special%20Powers%20Act.%20However%2C%20the%20Northeast%20and%20Kashmir%20are%20not%20the%20only%20places%20where%20such%20encounters%20happen%2C%20of%20course%2C%20and%20AFSPA%20is%20not%20necessary%20for%20the%20State%20to%20conduct%20%E2%80%9Cencounters%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EManipur%20is%20again%20in%20the%20news%20globally%2C%20but%20for%20other%20reasons.%20Here%20also%2C%20like%20with%20extrajudicial%20killings%2C%20as%20a%20people%20we%20have%20looked%20away%20from%20what%20has%20happened%20and%20even%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20was%20forced%20to%20speak%20only%20after%20an%20especially%20horrible%20incident%20came%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20has%20happened%20to%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20State%20in%20India%20after%20the%20government%20has%20accepted%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20that%20this%20sort%20of%20murder%20is%20a%20reality%3F%20Not%20much%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20and%20such%20encounters%20continue.%20The%20examples%20cited%20above%20of%20someone%20being%20killed%20in%20custody%20even%20after%20they%20went%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20and%20someone%20being%20killed%20while%20being%20transported%20and%20being%20covered%20live%20on%20TV%2C%20are%20quite%20recent.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20appears%20that%20there%20is%20a%20set%20of%20circumstances%20that%20makes%20this%20possible.%20At%20the%20level%20of%20society%2C%20there%20is%20not%20much%20pushback%20against%20such%20murders.%20This%20is%20speculation%20and%20anecdotal%2C%20but%20it%20appears%20to%20be%20the%20case%20that%20there%20is%20approval%20of%20the%20use%20of%20such%20methods%2C%20because%20of%20the%20idea%20of%20%E2%80%9Cgood%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cbad%E2%80%9D%20people.%20This%20is%20reflected%20in%20the%20media%20coverage%20of%20such%20incidents%2C%20where%20holding%20the%20State%20to%20account%20for%20extra-judicial%20murder%20is%20not%20the%20primary%20concern%20or%20point%20raised.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20this%20societal%20approval%2C%20or%20at%20least%20because%20of%20an%20absence%20of%20meaningful%20pushback%20except%20from%20what%20is%20called%20civil%20society%2C%20the%20government%20can%20continue%20doing%20what%20it%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThough%20it%20has%20taken%20some%20interest%20in%20the%20matter%2C%20the%20judiciary%20also%20has%20not%20held%20the%20State%20to%20account%20for%20what%20is%20has%20done%20in%20the%20past%20and%20what%20it%20continues%20to%20do.%20All%20of%20this%20has%20meant%20that%20extra-judicial%20killings%20in%20India%20remain%20quite%20normal.%20So%20long%20as%20this%20does%20not%20concern%20others%2C%20it%20has%20not%20been%20a%20problem.%20However%2C%20this%20month%2C%20the%20issue%20has%20become%20international.%20The%20Indian%20State%20is%20accused%20of%20an%20extra-judicial%20killing%20on%20someone%20else%E2%80%99s%20territory.%20No%20evidence%20of%20this%20has%20been%20put%20out%20so%20far%2C%20and%20we%20must%20as%20always%20take%20the%20position%20of%20presumed%20innocence.%20And%20we%20must%20hope%20that%20the%20allegations%20are%20untrue.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Vikas%20Dubey's%20Killing%20Reminds%20Punjab%20of%202%2C000%2B%20%E2%80%98Disappearances%E2%80%99%20During%20Insurgency%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpunjab-militancy-enforced-disappearances-fake-encounters%5C%22%3EVikas%20Dubey%E2%80%99s%20Killing%20Reminds%20Punjab%20of%202%2C000%2B%20%E2%80%98Disappearances%E2%80%99%20During%20Insurgency%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20we%20must%20also%20consider%20what%20the%20status%20is%20inside%20our%20home.%20The%20problem%20is%20amplified%20and%20endemic%20inside%20our%20country.%20An%20unofficial%20and%20brutal%20justice%20system%20exists%20parallel%20to%20the%20official%20one%2C%20and%20it%20executes%20many%20times%20more%20of%20the%20accused%20than%20the%20official%20one%20executes%20convicts.%20A%20report%20in%20The%20Hindu%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EFrontline%3C%2Fem%3E%20magazine%20last%20year%20said%20that%20between%202016%20and%202022%2C%20more%20than%20800%20encounter%20killings%20had%20been%20recorded.%20In%20the%20same%20period%2C%20the%20number%20of%20people%20hanged%20after%20conviction%20was%20five.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20should%20not%20take%20external%20pressure%20for%20us%20to%20look%20at%20ourselves%2C%20but%20that%20seems%20to%20be%20how%20things%20often%20move%20in%20India.%20The%20list%20of%20those%20executed%20in%20Manipur%20had%20been%20prepared%20and%20submitted%20to%20Christof%20Heyns%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20special%20rapporteur%20on%20extra-judicial%2C%20summary%20or%20arbitrary%20executions%2C%20who%20had%20come%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20India%20in%20March%202012.%20Should%20it%20have%20needed%20this%20before%20we%20acted%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAakar%20Patel%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20and%20columnist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%