h%2Fdespite-pli-cost-of-telecom-hardware-manufacturing-in-india-13-higher-than-china-trai%2Farticle67344050.ece%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%20BusinessLine%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETRAI%20noted%20that%20although%20exports%20have%20more%20than%20tripled%20to%20Rs%2076%2C469%20crore%20since%20the%20scheme%20started%2C%20the%20same%20cannot%20be%20said%20for%20what%20the%20regulator%20categorises%20as%20%E2%80%98Type%202%E2%80%99%20telecom%20products.%20These%20are%20products%20which%20are%20utilised%20by%20operators%20to%20set%20up%20their%20telecommunication%20networks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20Department%20of%20Telecommunications%20extended%20subsidies%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9CType%202%E2%80%9D%20category%20of%20products%20to%2042%20companies-%20the%20results%20are%20far%20more%20limited%2C%20exports%20increased%20by%20only%2030%20crore%20%E2%80%93%20during%20the%20first%20year%20of%20the%20subsidy%20scheme%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20significant%20disparity%20in%20manufacturing%20costs%20between%20countries%20like%20China%2C%20Vietnam%2C%20and%20India%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20various%20factors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20TRAI%20observed%20that%20China%20offers%20programmes%20like%20%E2%80%9CHigh-%20and%20New-Technology%20Enterprise%20(HNTE)%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CMade%20in%20China%202025%E2%80%9D%20that%20provide%20multiple%20benefits%20to%20companies%20engaged%20in%20technological%20fields%2C%20including%20electronics%20production.%20These%20programmes%20encourage%20investments%20into%20research%20and%20development%20(R%26amp%3BD).%20They%20also%20encourage%20low-end%20manufacturers%20to%20transition%20into%20high-end%20goods%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20Vietnam%20provides%20incentives%20such%20as%20reduced%20corporate%20taxes%20for%20manufacturers%20and%20lower%20import%20duties%20on%20components.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20subsidy%20schemes%20focus%20on%20providing%20incentives%20on%20the%20number%20of%20finished%20goods%20produced.%20In%20addition%2C%20India%20dissuades%20the%20import%20of%20finished%20products%20by%20bumping%20up%20import%20duties%20on%20fully%20assembled%20goods%20such%20as%20smartphones%20or%20networking%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20the%20regulatory%20authority%20has%20recommended%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20move%20beyond%20the%20PLI%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBuilding%20local%20value%20addition%20incentives%20into%20its%20subsidy%20schemes%20to%20avail%20any%20benefits%20from%20the%20PLI%20is%20one%20of%20the%20suggestions%20by%20TRAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20addition%20to%20the%20already%20announced%201%25%20additional%20benefit%2C%20another%20slab%20of%20additional%202%25%20benefit%20%5Bcan%5D%20be%20introduced%20for%20product%20lines%20that%20yield%20minimum%20local%20value-addition%20of%2075%25%E2%80%A6%2C%E2%80%9D%20in%20reference%20to%20the%20design-led%20PLI%20scheme%20for%20network%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20TRAI%20also%20wants%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20start%20rolling%20out%20PLI%20schemes%20for%20components%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695710714000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2F527222-telecom.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdespite-pli-manufacturing-telecom-hardware-in-india-is-12-13-costlier-than-china-trai-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22TRAI%20noted%20that%20although%20exports%20have%20more%20than%20tripled%20to%20Rs%2076%2C469%20crore%20since%20the%20PLI%20scheme%20started%2C%20the%20same%20cannot%20be%20said%20for%20what%20the%20regulator%20categorises%20as%20%E2%80%98Type%202'%20telecom%20products.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdespite-pli-manufacturing-telecom-hardware-in-india-is-12-13-costlier-than-china-trai-repor