20-February%202021%20period%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20fill%20up%20an%20online%20form%20or%20send%20an%20email%20with%20the%20details.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fpress-council-of-india-sets-up-committee-to-study-retrenchment-of-journalists-during-pandemic%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Woman%20Killed%20Mother%20By%20Stabbing%20Her%20After%20She%20Was%20Kicked%20Out%20Of%20College%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2023-year-old%20woman%20from%20Ohio%20killed%20her%20mother%20by%20beating%20her%20with%20an%20iron%20skillet%20and%20stabbing%20her%20nearly%2030%20times%20in%20the%20neck-%20because%20she%20learned%20she'd%20been%20kicked%20out%20of%20college%20and%20didn't%20want%20her%20mother%20to%20find%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprosecutor.summitoh.net%2Fnews%2F31917%2Fonly_pdf%2Fsydney-powell-jury-guilty-092023.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESummit%20County%20Prosecutor's%20Office%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Sydney%20Powell%20of%20Akron%20was%20found%20guilty%20of%20murder%2C%20felonious%20assault%20and%20tampering%20with%20evidence%20in%20the%20brutal%20death%20of%20healthcare%20worker%20Brenda%20Powell%2C%2050.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20March%20of%202020%2C%20Sydney%20Powell%20struck%20Brenda%20Powell%20in%20the%20head%20with%20an%20iron%20skillet%2C%20then%20stabbed%20her%20nearly%2030%20times%20in%20the%20neck%2C%26quot%3B%20Summit%20County%20Prosecutor's%20Office%20said%20in%20a%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAkron%20Beacon%20Journal%20reported%20that%20Powell%2C%20a%20former%20Mount%20Union%20University%20student%2C%20sobbed%20in%20the%20Summit%20County%20Common%20Pleas%20courtroom%20after%20a%20jury%20found%20her%20guilty%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20March%203%2C%202020%2C%20police%20found%20Brenda%20inside%20her%20Scudder%20Drive%20home%20with%20severe%20injuries.%20She%20was%20rushed%20to%20the%20hospital%20where%20she%20died%20from%20her%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2023%2F09%2F25%2Fsydney-powell-killed-mom-with-frying-pan-knife-over-college-secret%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20report%2C%20Powell%20attacked%20her%20mother-%20a%20child%20life%20specialist%20at%20Akron%20Children's%20Hospital%20-%20while%20she%20was%20on%20the%20phone%20with%20officials%20from%20her%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20defence%20argued%20that%20Powell%20suffered%20from%20schizophrenia%20and%20therefore%20could%20not%20be%20held%20accountable%20for%20the%20murder%2C%20the%20media%20outlet%20reported.%20James%20Reardon%2C%20one%20of%20three%20defence%20experts%20who%20made%20the%20diagnosis%2C%20said%20Sydney%20suffered%20a%20psychotic%20break%20when%20she%20killed%20her%20mom%2C%20whom%20she%20had%20considered%20her%20best%20friend.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESylvia%20O'Bradovich%2C%20a%20psychologist%20hired%20by%20prosecutors%20disagreed%20with%20the%20diagnosis%20and%20said%20Powell%20did%20not%20meet%20the%20legal%20definition%20of%20insanity%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20crime.%20Ms%20O'Bradovich%20agreed%20that%20Powell%20suffers%20from%20mental%20health%20issues%2C%20including%20borderline%20personality%20traits%2C%20malingering%20and%20an%20anxiety%20disorder.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDescribing%20the%20incident%20in%20court%2C%20Assistant%20Prosecutor%20Brian%20Stano%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSydney%20stopped%20attacking%20with%20the%20pan%2C%20presumably%20went%20to%20the%20kitchen%20with%20a%20knife%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20the%20Akron%20Beacon%20Journal.%20%26quot%3BShe%20had%20to%20switch%20weapons%20and%20keep%20attacking%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20Stano%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20the%20knife%20just%20in%20the%20neck%20multiple%20times%3F%20That%20is%20purposeful%2C%26quot%3B%20Stano%20added.%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%20trying%20to%20end%20someone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPowell's%20sentencing%20is%20scheduled%20for%20Sept.%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695708600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fdnf786h8_sydney-powell_625x300_26_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-woman-killed-mother-by-stabbing-her-30-times-after-she-discovered-her-college-secret-police-4424195%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sydney%20Powell%20of%20Akron%20was%20found%20guilty%20of%20murder%2C%20felonious%20assault%20and%20tampering%20with%20evidence%20in%20the%20death%20of%20healthcare%20worker%20Brenda%20Powell%2C%2050.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-woman-killed-mother-by-stabbing-her-30-times-after-she-discovered-her-college-secret-police-4424195%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-woman-killed-mother-by-stabbing-her-30-times-after-she-discovered-her-college-secret-police-4424195%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-woman-killed-mother-by-stabbing-her-30-times-after-she-discovered-her-college-secret-police-4424195%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Asian%20Games%20Sailing%3A%20Neha%20Thakur%20clinches%20silver%2C%20Eabad%20Ali%20gets%20bronze%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695708236000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103958508%2Cimgsize-64288.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fasian-games-2023%2Findia-asian-games%2Fasian-games-indias-sailor-neha-thakur-wins-silver-medal-in-sailing%2Farticleshow%2F103951509.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20sailor%20Neha%20Thakur%20has%20won%20a%20silver%20medal%20in%20the%20girl's%20dinghy%20ILCA-4%20event%20at%20the%20Asian%20Games.%20Thakur%2C%20representing%20the%20National%20Sailing%20School%20in%20Bhopal