m%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Eissued%20fresh%20notices%20to%20BBC%20(UK)%20and%20BBC%20(India)%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20NGO%2C%20Justice%20on%20Trial%2C%20claimed%20that%20the%20BBC%E2%80%99s%20documentary%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20%3Cem%3EIndia%3A%20The%20Modi%20Question%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20has%20damaged%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20reputation%20and%20made%20%E2%80%9Cfalse%20and%20defamatory%20imputations%E2%80%9D%20against%20him%20as%20well%20as%20the%20judiciary.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%2C%20comprising%20Justice%20Sachin%20Datta%2C%C2%A0has%20listed%20the%20matter%20for%20December%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20counsel%20for%20the%20petitioner%20NGO%20informed%20the%20single-judge%20bench%20that%20notices%20had%20been%20issued%20to%20BBC%20(UK)%20and%20BBC%20(India)%20earlier%20but%20could%20not%20be%20served%20and%20sought%20more%20time%20to%20serve%20these%2C%20the%3Cem%3E%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20(TOI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdelhi%2Fdocumentary-on-modi-delhi-hc-issues-fresh-notices-to-bbc%2Farticleshow%2F103947207.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20British%20broadcaster%20had%20released%20a%20two-part%20documentary%20series%20on%20the%20Gujarat%20riots%20that%20happened%20when%20Modi%20was%20chief%20minister%20of%20the%20state.%20The%20government%20had%20asked%20platforms%20to%20remove%20links%20to%20the%20documentary%20soon%20after%20its%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fexclusive-vajpayee-govt-didnt-object-to-uk-report-that-2002-riots-were-pre-planned-cops-told-not-to-act%5C%22%3EExclusive%3A%20Vajpayee%20Govt%20Didn%E2%80%99t%20Object%20to%20UK%20Report%20That%202002%20Riots%20Were%20%E2%80%98Pre-Planned%E2%80%99%2C%20Cops%20%E2%80%98Told%20Not%20to%20Act%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner%20has%20sought%20damages%20of%20Rs%