ix%20weeks%2C%20but%20I%20miss%20you.%20Kya%20karoon%2C%20Dads%20worry%20about%20daughters.%20I%20hope%20'Kanneda'%2C%20as%20us%20Punjabis%20say%2C%20is%20treating%20you%20well.%20But%20that's%20a%20slightly%20loaded%20question%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20right%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI'm%20writing%20because%20after%20our%20video%20call%20last%20night%2C%20I%20could%20see%20that%20the%20recent%20stuff%20that's%20happened%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%20over%20the%20Harjeet%20Nijjar%20killing%2C%20which%20should%20actually%20not%20affect%20students%20like%20you%20at%20all%2C%20is%20making%20you%20and%20your%20classmates%20a%20bit%20anxious.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20you%20know%2C%20in%20June%202023%2C%20this%20Indian-born%20Canadian%20Sikh%2C%20Harjeet%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20was%20shot%20dead%20at%20a%20gurudwara%20near%20Vancouver.%20Nijjar%20was%20an%20outspoken%20Khalistan%20(demands%20for%20a%20separate%20'Sikh%20nation'%20to%20be%20carved%20out%20in%20India%2C%20look%20it%20up)%20supporter.%20So%20India%20considered%20him%20a%20separatist%2C%20and%20also%20a%20terrorist%20because%20he%20allegedly%20master-minded%20several%20killings%20in%20India%2C%20heading%20his%20own%20terror%20group%20-the%20Khalistan%20Tiger%20Force.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Canada%20has%20allowed%20Khalistan%20supporters%2C%20many%20now%20Canadian%20citizens%2C%20to%20speak%20their%20mind%2C%20citing%20freedom%20of%20speech.%20They've%20ignored%20India's%20claims%20that%20some%20of%20them%20have%20been%20responsible%20for%20extremist%20violence%20in%20Punjab.%20Also%2C%20many%20Sikhs%20in%20Canadian%20politics%20back%20the%20Khalistan%20sentiment%20to%20get%20Sikh%20votes.%20One%20of%20them%20is%20Jagmeet%20'Jimmy'%20Dhaliwal%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20New%20Democratic%20Party%20(NDP).%20Since%20Justin%20Trudeau's%20Liberal%20Party%20does%20not%20have%20a%20majority%20in%20Canada's%20parliament%2C%20it%20depends%20on%20NDP's%20support%20to%20stay%20in%20power.%20Political%20experts%20in%20Canada%20and%20India%20say%20this%20has%20put%20pressure%20on%20Trudeau%20to%20look%20away%20from%20the%20radical%20activities%20of%20Canada's%20Khalistani%20separatists.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYou%20now%20have%20some%20context%2C%20so%20let's%20return%20to%20what's%20happened%20-%20Justin%20Trudeau%20publicly%20accusing%20India%20of%20a%20role%20in%20killing%20Nijjar.%20It's%20big%2C%20because%20we%20are%20friendly%20countries.%20Also%2C%20India%20has%20never%20been%20accused%20of%20something%20like%20this%20-%20killing%20a%20citizen%20of%20a%20friendly%20country%2C%20on%20that%20country's%20soil.%20It's%20become%20a%20full%20on%20diplomatic%20spat.%20We've%20expelled%20each%20other's%20diplomats%2C%20India%20has%20suspended%20visas%20for%20Canadians%2C%20and%20told%20Indian%20citizens%20(yes%2C%20you)%20in%20Canada%20to%20be%20cautious.%20Top%20BJP%20leaders%20in%20India%20have%20accused%20Canada%20of%20%26quot%3Bsupporting%20terrorists%26quot%3B%20on%20its%20soil%20for%20years.%20On%20this%20issue%2C%20even%20opposition%20parties%20in%20India%20are%20criticizing%20Canada%20and%20Trudeau.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20it's%20messed%20up.%20But%20you%20know%20what%20-%20YOU%20are%20the%20key%20to%20solving%20this%20whole%20problem.%20Ira%20Khanna%20can%20set%20this%20right!%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhy%20do%20I%20say%20so%3F%20Because%20you%2C%20my%20dear%2C%20are%20the%20future%20of%20Canada%20and%20India's%20relationship.%20You%20and%203.2%20lakh%20other%20Indian%20students%20who%20are%20studying%20in%20Canada%20right%20now.%20For%20anyone%20who%20believes%20that%20the%20United%20States%20is%20the%20preferred%20destination%20for%20Indian%20students%2C%20they%20are%20wrong.%20It's%20Canada.%20The%20US%20has%202.2%20lakh%20students%2C%20a%20big%20number%2C%20but%20way%20behind%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20I'll%20tell%20you%20what%2C%20while%20higher%20fees%20is%20one%20factor%20against%20the%20US%2C%20the%20other%20factor%20is%20-%20safety.%20With%20news%20breaking%20every%20few%20days%20of%20deadly%20shootings%20on%20US%20school%20and%20college%20campuses%2C%20and%20also%20malls%20and%20other%20public%20places%2C%20families%20are%20not%20sure%20their%20children%20will%20be%20safe%20there.%20But%20Canada%20is%20considered%20safe.%20There%20is%20also%20the%20feeling%20that%20racism%20is%20higher%20in%20America.%20Just%20days%20ago%2C%20we%20all%20saw%20the%20news%20about%20the%20Seattle%20cop%20who%20joked%20about%20the%20death%20of%2023%20year-old%20student%20Jaahnavi%20Kandula%2C%20who%20was%20hit%20and%20killed%20by%20a%20Seattle%20Police%20vehicle%20in%20January.%20His%20bodycam%20audio%20showed%20him%20laughing%20and%20saying%20that%20Jaahnavi%20'had%20limited%20value'%2C%20revealing%20a%20fairly%20sick%20racist%20attitude.%20On%20racism%2C%20and%20on%20sectarian%20harmony%20too%2C%20the%20perception%20is%20that%20Canada%20is%20safer%2C%20more%20tolerant%2C%20more%20respectful.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what's%20the%20message%20for%20Monsieur%20Trudeau%3F%20Simple%20-%20hold%20on%20to%20this%20advantage%20and%20keep%20Canada%20safe%20and%20welcoming.%20It's%20also%20good%20business%20sense.%20Data%20released%20by%20Immigration%2C%20Refugees%20and%20Citizenship%20Canada%20(IRCC)%20shows%20that%20in%202022%20Canada%20had%208.1%20lakh%20foreign%20students%2C%20and%20that%20in%202022%20alone%2C%20they%20issued%20study%20permits%20to%20a%20record%205.5%20lakh%20foreign%20students%2C%20from%20184%20countries.%20That%20is%20not%20just%20a%20lot%20of%20trust%2C%20it's%20also%20millions%20of%20dollars%20in%20tuition%20fees.%20Literally%2C%20thousands%20of%20Canadian%20jobs%20are%20created%2C%20thousands%20of%20Canadian%20businesses%20thrive%20thanks%20to%20foreign%20students.%20And%20'job%20creation'%20is%20one%20of%20the%20surest%20ways%20to%20win%20an%20election%20in%20Canada.%20So%2C%20Trudeau%20needs%20to%20say%20this%20every%20night%20before%20going%20to%20sleep%20-%20'I%20need%20to%20make%20Canada%20a%20safer%20place%20for%20Ira%20Khanna%2C%20or%20else...'%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20and%20I%20am%20being%20truly%20objective%20here%2C%20I%20think%20Canada%20has%20cut%20the%20pro-Khalistan%20extremists%20more%20slack%20than%20their%20law%20permits.%20Some%20months%20ago%2C%20pro-Khalistanis%20had%20a%20procession%20which%20included%20a%20float%20that%20celebrated%20India's%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20assassination.%20I%20would%20not%20call%20that%20'freedom%20of%20expression'.%20That's%20hate.%20Some%20pro-Khalistan%20activists%20have%20issued%20death%20threats%20to%20Indian%20diplomats%2C%20there%20have%20been%20incidents%20of%20Hindu%20temples%20being%20vandalized%2C%20and%20more%20recently%20a%20radical%20named%20Gurpatwant%20Pannu%20issued%20threats%20to%20Canadian%20Hindus%20that%20they%20should%20leave%20Canada.%20Surely%20much%20of%20this%20is%20against%20Canadian%20law%2C%20but%20we%20have%20not%20seen%20the%20police%20take%20much%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGangsters%20based%20in%20Canada%2C%20apart%20from%20committing%20crimes%20in%20Canada%2C%20have%20also%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20killings%20in%20India.%20A%20gangster%20named%20Goldy%20Brar%20has%20accepted%20in%20telephonic%20interviews%20to%20Indian%20media%20that%20he%20was%20behind%20the%20killing%20of%20rapper%20Sidhu%20Moosewala%20in%20Punjab%20in%20May%202022.%20It%20should%20worry%20Trudeau%20that%20today%20some%20of%20the%20most%20notorious%20crime%20cartels%20in%20Canada%20are%20of%20Punjabi%20and%20Sikh%20origin.%20Tomorrow%2C%20(and%20it%20may%20already%20be%20happening)%20these%20gangs%20could%20link%20up%20with%20the%20Khalistani%20separatists%2C%20and%20provide%20them%20money%20and%20arms.%20This%20has%20happened%20in%20India%2C%20with%20the%20underworld%20don%20Dawood%20Ibrahim%20collaborating%20with%20Islamic%20terror%20groups%20to%20commit%20deadly%20attacks%20in%20India.%20It's%20something%20that%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20violence%20within%20Canada%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20yes%2C%20Trudeau%20ji%20has%20a%20lot%20to%20think%20about.%20Seriously.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIra%2C%20you%20may%20go%20on%20to%20build%20a%20career%20and%20a%20life%20in%20Canada%2C%20and%20I%20would%20really%20be%20happy%20if%20that%20happened.%20Even%20today%2C%20despite%20the%20aberration%20created%20by%20this%20spat%20with%20India%2C%20the%20fact%20remains%20that%20Canada%20is%20indeed%20one%20of%20the%20most%20liveable%20countries%20in%20the%20world.%20Folks%20earn%20well%2C%20the%20government%20machinery%20is%20not%20corrupt%2C%20it's%20responsive%20and%20accountable.%20Citizens%20are%20cared%20for.%20The%20cities%20are%20clean%2C%20pollution%20levels%20are%20low%2C%20people%20are%20polite%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20spectacularly%20beautiful%20country%2C%20so%20what's%20not%20to%20love%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20just%20hope%20that%20those%20who%20control%20Canada%20today%20don't%20just%20think%20of%20political%20survival%20today.%20I%20hope%2C%20for%20your%20sake%2C%20that%20they%20also%20have%20a%20vision%20of%20Canada's%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELots%20of%20Love%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPapa%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Rohit%20Khanna%20is%20a%20journalist%2C%20commentator%20and%20video%20storyteller.%20He%20has%20been%20Managing%20Editor%20at%20The%20Quint%2C%20Executive%20Producer%20of%20Investigations%20%26amp%3B%20Special%20Projects%20at%20CNN-IBN%2C%20and%20is%20a%202-time%20Ramnath%20Goenka%20award%20winner)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695706260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F2dpvcot8_toronto-generic_625x300_26_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Fblog-letter-to-my-daughter-in-canada-4424039%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Over%20the%20years%2C%20Canada%20has%20allowed%20Khalistan%20supporters%2C%20many%20now%20Canadian%20cit