mes%20Down%20Heavily%20on%20UP%20Govt%2C%20Police%20for%20Handling%20of%20Muzaffarnagar%20Slapping%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28095821%2FUntitled-design-2-3.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Monday%20(September%2025)%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20and%20police%20for%20their%20handling%20of%20the%20Muzaffarnagar%20case%20in%20which%20a%20teacher%20encouraged%20other%20students%20to%20repeatedly%20slap%20a%20young%20Muslim%20boy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20cited%20the%20delay%20in%20registering%20an%20FIR%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20reference%20to%20allegations%20of%20communal%20hatred%20in%20it%2C%20and%20said%20that%20the%20case%20must%20be%20investigated%20by%20a%20senior%20IPS%20police%20officer%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-muzaffarnagar-child-slapping-uttar-pradesh-police-quality-education-rte-act-238610%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20The%20case%20was%20heard%20by%20a%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Abhay%20S.%20Oka%20and%20Justice%20Pankaj%20Mithal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20take%20serious%20objections%20to%20the%20way%20the%20FIR%20was%20filed.%20The%20father%20had%20made%20a%20statement%20saying%20allegations%20were%20made%20and%20he%20was%20beaten%20due%20to%20religion.%20But%20this%20is%20not%20mentioned%20in%20the%20FIR.%20Next%20is%2C%20where%20is%20video%20transcript%3F%20This%20is%20about%20quality%20education.%20Quality%20education%20includes%20sensitive%20education.%20The%20manner%20in%20which%20it%20has%20happened%20should%20shake%20the%20conscience%20of%20the%20State%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Oka%20said%20in%20court%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fsupreme-court-allegations-fir-muzaffarnagar-teacher-students-slap-muslim-child%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdditional%20Solicitor%20General%20(ASG)%20K.M.%20Nataraj%2C%20representing%20the%20UP%20government%2C%20claimed%20in%20court%20that%20the%20communal%20angle%20had%20been%20%E2%80%9Cblown%20out%20of%20proportion%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20communal%20angle%20blown%20out%20of%20proportion.%20Something%20is%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNot%20just%20something%2C%20it%20is%20very%20serious.%20The%20teacher%20gave%20mandate%20to%20beat%20the%20child%20because%20of%20his%20religion.%20What%20kind%20of%20education%20is%20being%20imparted%3F%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Oka%20responded.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20said%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Cprima%20facie%20failure%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20State%E2%80%9D%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20mandate%20of%20the%20Right%20to%20Education%20Act%20that%20prohibits%20the%20mental%20and%20physical%20harassment%20of%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20a%20long%20delay%20an%20FIR%20has%20been%20registered%20on%20September%206%2C%202023%2C%20alleging%20commission%20of%20offences%20under%20Section%2075%20of%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Act%2C%202015%2C%20and%20Sections%20323%C2%A0(voluntarily%20causing%20hurt)%C2%A0and%20503%C2%A0(criminal%20intimidation)%C2%A0of%20the%20IPC%20have%20been%20invoked.%20Petitioner%20contends%20offence%20is%20also%20of%2075(2)%20of%20JJ%20Act%20and%20153A%C2%A0(promoting%20enmity%20between%20different%20groups)%20of%20the%20IPC.%20The%20probe%20shall%20be%20supervised%20by%20a%20senior%20police%20officer%20nominated%20by%20the%20State%20government%20to%20look%20into%20whether%20these%20two%20offences%20deserve%20to%20be%20invoked.%20The%20IPS%20officer%20so%20invited%20shall%20submit%20a%20report%20to%20this%20court%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20ordered.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%20hearing%20a%20PIL%20filed%20by%20activist%20Tushar%20Gandhi%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20that%20went%20viral%20in%20August%2C%20a%20teacher%20named%20Tripta%20Tyagi%20who%20runs%20%E2%80%98Neha%20Public%20School%E2%80%99%20at%20her%20home%20can%20be%20seen%20exhorting%20the%20students%20to%20assault%20a%20child%20who%20is%20seen%20crying%20while%20different%20students%20come%20forward%C2%A0%20to%20slap%20him.%20At%20one%20point%20in%20the%20video%2C%20the%20teacher%20scolded%20a%20student%20for%20not%20hitting%20him%20hard%20enough.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20declared%20that%20all%20those%20Muslim%20children%20should%20be%E2%80%A6(inaudible)%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20can%20be%20heard%20saying%20in%20the%20forty-second%20long%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695700781000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28095821%2FUntitled-design-2-3.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-comes-down-heavily-on-up-govt-police-for-handling-of-muzaffarnagar-slapping-case%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20court%20cited%20the%20delay%20in%20registering%20an%20FIR%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20reference%20to%20allegations%20of%20communal%20hatred%20in%20it%2C%20and%20said%20that%20the%20case%20must%20be%20investigated%20by%20a%20senior%20IPS%20police%20officer.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A30%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-comes-down-heavily-on-up-govt-police-for-handling-of-muzaffarnagar-slapping-case%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'America's%20natural%20ally'%3A%20Five%20things%20JPMorgan%20chief%20Dimon%20said%20about%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695700724000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-04%2F07%2Ffull%2F1680837772-3453.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Famerica-s-natural-ally-five-things-jpmorgan-chief-dimon-said-ab