aran%20expresses%20how%20the%20BJP%20may%20defend%20sanatana%20dharma%20without%20defining%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20logical%20question%20that%20arises%20is%2C%20how%20can%20one%20defend%20something%20not%20knowing%20what%20they%20are%20defending%3F%20But%20this%20is%20exactly%20how%20the%20BJP%20is%20defending%20its%20%3Cem%3Eposition%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20this%20controversy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20was%20the%20%3Cem%3Eposition%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20a%20particular%20brand%20of%20Hinduism%20that%20emerged%20in%20the%2019th-century%20history%20of%20India%2C%20where%20orthodoxy%20became%20a%20signifier%20of%20such%20a%20brand.%20The%20BJP%20seems%20to%20be%20asserting%20that%20particular%20%3Cem%3Eposition%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20sanatana%20dharma%2C%20a%20position%20that%20captures%20an%20orthodoxy%20and%20regressiveness%20in%20the%20name%20of%20tradition%2C%20and%20one%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3ESangh%20parivar%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20so%20anxious%20to%20preserve.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20should%20come%20as%20no%20surprise%20that%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20it%20is%20this%20%3Cem%3Eposition%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20orthodoxy%20that%20matters%3B%20sanatana%20dharma%E2%80%99s%20meanings%20and%20definitions%20do%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20sharp%20exchange%20between%20Udhayanidhi%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20particularly%20of%20their%20IT%20cell%20chief%20Amit%20Malviya%20on%20this%20issue%2C%20foregrounds%20a%20%3Cem%3Emeaning-position%3C%2Fem%3E%20dichotomy%20of%20the%20phrase%20%E2%80%98sanatana%20dharma%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20i.e.%20it%20points%20up%20the%20wide%20gap%20between%20the%20understanding%20of%20the%20pre-19th%20century%20%3Cem%3Emeaning%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20phrase%20and%20its%2019th%20century%20%3Cem%3Eposition%20%3C%2Fem%3Eas%20a%20signifier%20of%20orthodoxy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKnowing%20that%20this%20position%20is%20embarrassing%20to%20defend%2C%20sanatana%20dharma%20is%20often%20couched%20in%20terms%20of%20moral%20values%20and%20defended%20by%20maintaining%20an%20elevated%20tone.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20a%20judge%20of%20the%20Madras%20high%20court%2C%20Justice%20N.%20Seshasayee%2C%20seems%20to%20have%20adopted%20such%20a%20tone%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20present%20controversy%2C%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftamil-nadu%2Fsanatana-dharma-is-a-set-of-eternal-duties-must-they-be-destroyed-asks-madras-hc-judge%2Farticle67312902.ece%5C%22%3Eposing%20a%20series%20of%20rhetorical%20questions%20%3C%2Fa%3Eas%3A%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CShould%20not%20a%20citizen%20love%20his%20country%3F%20Is%20he%20not%20under%20a%20duty%20to%20serve%20his%20nation%3F%20Should%20not%20the%20parents%20be%20cared%20for%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20package%20of%20such%20common%20sense%20human%20values%2C%20responsibilities%20of%20an%20individual%20and%20standards%20of%20behaviour%20and%20conduct%20is%20brought%20forward%2C%20labelled%20as%20sanatana%20dharma%20and%20then%20defended.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fwhat-is-sanatana-dharma%5C%22%3EWhat%20Is%20Sanatana%20Dharma%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUdhayanidhi%E2%80%99s%20sharp%20criticism%20of%20sanatana%20dharma%20was%20definitely%20not%20against%20such%20values%2C%20but%20was%20actually%20directed%20against%20the%20position%20of%20orthodoxy%2C%20a%20position%20that%20underlies%20the%20politics%20of%20Hindu%20nationalism%20or%20the%20Hindu%20%3Cem%3Erashtra%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20be%20significant%20to%20understand%20the%20kinds%20of%20meanings%20associated%20with%20this%20phrase%20%E2%80%98sanatana%20dharma%E2%80%99%2C%20very%20briefly%2C%20and%20see%20the%20distinction%20between%20this%20understanding%20and%20the%20position%20adopted%20by%20the%20Hindu%20orthodoxy%20of%20the%2019th%20century%2C%20in%20which%20the%20phrase%20got%20appropriated%20to%20refer%20to%20Hinduism%20in%20its%20entirety.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMeanings%20of%20sanatana%20dharma%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVaishali%20Jayaraman%2C%20a%20scholar%2C%20has%20given%20an%20exhaustive%20coverage%20of%20the%20various%20meanings%20of%20sanatana%20dharma%20and%20the%20contexts%20of%20its%20use%20from%20her%20study%20of%20Sanskrit%20classical%20literature%20like%20the%20%3Cem%3EMahabharata%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ERamayana%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EPuranas%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3EDharmashastras%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20she%2C%20who%20appears%20to%20be%20favourably%20oriented%20towards%20this%20pre-19th%20century%20concept%20of%20sanatana%20dharma%2C%20notes%20that%20the%20concept%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frepositories.lib.utexas.edu%2Fbitstream%2Fhandle%2F2152%2F76283%2FSan%25C4%2581tanadharma%2520in%2520Sanskrit%2520Literature.pdf%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cvague%20in%20the%20extent%20of%20its%20definition%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20find%20a%20uniform%20meaning%20in%20her%20analysis%20of%20classical%20texts.%20Further%2C%20the%20phrase%20has%20never%20been%20used%20as%20a%20self-description%20or%20characterisation%20of%20any%20one%20religious%20group%20or%20tradition%20among%20many%20in%20these%20texts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20connotation%20of%20the%20phrase%20%E2%80%98sanatana%20dharma%E2%80%99%20in%20these%20classical%20texts%2C%20and%20the%20following%20marks%20its%20semantic%20variations%20(for%20a%20detailed%20textual%20analysis%20of%20meaning%20one%20can%20see%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frepositories.lib.utexas.edu%2Fbitstream%2Fhandle%2F2152%2F76283%2FSan%25C4%2581tanadharma%2520in%2520Sanskrit%2520Literature.pdf%3Fsequence%3D2%26isAllowed%3Dy%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20just%20list%20out%20some)%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3Ea)%20Social%20etiquette%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3Eb)%20Denotes%20a%20list%20of%20duties%20of%20the%20king%20with%20several%20dos%20and%20don%E2%80%99ts%20he%20should%20follow.%20The%20protection%20of%20%3Cem%3Evarnashrama%20%3C%2Fem%3Edharma%20(a%20rigid%20social%20order%20of%20four%20castes%20where%20the%20lowest%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Eshudra%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20serves%20the%20three%20higher%20castes%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3Ebrahmin%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekshatriya%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Evaishya%3C%2Fem%3E)%20is%20one%20of%20his%20very%20important%20duties.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3Ec)%20It%20is%20constituted%20by%20a%20mix%20of%20different%20dharmas%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3Ed)%20Principles%20of%20a%20specific%20concept%2C%20like%20truth%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3Ee)%20A%20social%20norm%20that%20enables%20one%20to%20act%20according%20to%20a%20set%20of%20rules%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3Ef)%20A%20general%20principle%20or%20a%20universally%20accepted%20value%20for%20an%20individual%20to%20follow%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3Eg)%20A%20general%20way%20of%20the%20world%2C%20an%20observation%20or%20truth%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3Eh)%20Duties%20and%20responsibilities%20of%20an%20individual%20at%20both%20a%20personal%20and%20professional%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fsaakhi-the-santana-dharma-on-caste-dissent-and-democracy%5C%22%3ESaakhi%3A%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20on%20Caste%2C%20Dissent%20and%20Democracy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EMahabharata%3C%2Fem%3E%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20provide%20a%20synoptic%20account%20of%20sanatana%20dharma.%20This%20phrase%2C%20as%20a%20philosophical%20and%20ethical%20concept%2C%20was%20also%20not%20taken%20up%20for%20critical%20reflection.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20classical%20literature%20of%20earlier%20times%2C%20sanatana%20dharma%20carries%20various%20connotations%2C%20with%20emphasis%20on%20the%20idea%20of%20the%20rigid%20social%20hierarchical%20order%20of%20caste.%20Later%2C%20in%20the%2019th%20century%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Esanatani%3C%2Fem%3E%20movement%20gained%20significance%20from%20the%20traditionalist%E2%80%99s%20encounter%20with%20the%20missionaries%20and%20the%20Hindu%20reformers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOrthodoxy%20of%20Sanatana%20Dharma%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20classical%20literature%2C%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20was%20never%20a%20term%20of%20self-description%20or%20self-assertion%20signifying%20a%20religious%20identity.%20Nor%20does%20this%20phrase%20mark%20a%20constituency%20holding%20a%20certain%20religious%20position%20before%20the%20late%2019th%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPandit%20Shraddha%20Ram%20Phillauri%20and%20Pandit%20Din%20Dayalu%20Sharma%20were%20the%20two%20leaders%20who%20pitched%20aggressively%20the%20idea%20of%20the%20orthodox%20brand%20of%20Hinduism%20as%20sanatana%20dharma.%20Their%20opponents%20were%2C%20primarily%2C%20Hindu%20reformists%20and%20Christian%20missionaries.%20As%20Kenneth%20W.%20Jones%2C%20a%20distinguished%20scholar%20of%20South%20Asian%20history%2C%20notes%20in%20his%20essay%2C%20%E2%80%9CTwo%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20Leaders%20and%20Swami%20Vivekananda%3A%20A%20Comparison%E2%80%9D%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20nineteenth%20century%2C%20there%20arose%20throughout%20British%20India%20a%20series%20of%20religious%20movements%20that%20can%20loosely%20be%20labelled%20as%20defensive%20of%20the%20various%20religious%20traditions%20then%20dominant.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20Hindus%20such%20groups%20were%20classed%20as%20%E2%80%98Sanatanists%E2%80%99%2C%20defenders%20of%20%3Cem%3Esanatana%20dharma%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20Eternal%20Religion.%20They%20saw%20themselves%20as%20champions%20of%20orthodoxy%20who%20fought%20all%20attempts%20at%20religious%20and%20social%20reform.%20Sanatanists%20have%20also%20been%20labelled%20as%20opponents%20of%20change%2C%20enemies%20of%20%E2%80%98modernisation%E2%80%99%20and%20Westernisation%2C%20thus%20reactionaries%20attempting%20to%20stem%20the%20tide%20of%20history.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShraddha%20Ram%20very%20strongly%20advocated%20for%20the%20caste%20system%20and%20also%20the%20idea%20of%20untouchability%20that%20follows%20from%20it.%20He%20uses%20the%20term%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Edwij%20dharm%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20three%20upper%20castes%20and%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Eneech%20admi%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20shudras.%20The%20extent%20of%20his%20extremely%20toxic%20and%20regressive%20views%20can%20be%20gauged%20from%20what%20he%20says%20in%20one%20instance%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMeeting%2C%20touching%2C%20eating%2C%20drinking%20with%20them%20is%20forbidden%20in%20our%20%3Cem%3Eshastras%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Should%20we%20meet%20them%20through%20force%2C%20or%20need%20or%20error%2C%20then%20doing%20%3Cem%3Eprayaschit%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5Batonement%5D%20is%20necessary.%20Then%20as%20far%20as%20possible%20we%20Hindus%20should%20remain%20distant%20from%20them.%E2%80%9D%20(quoted%20from%20the%20above%20essay%20of%20Kenneth%20W.%20Jones).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20views%20of%20Sharma%2C%20the%20other%20leader%2C%20in%20this%20regard%20are%20no%20different.%20This%20was%20the%20orthodox%20position%20that%20was%20defended%20as%20sanatana%20dharma.%20The%20signifier%20was%20the%20orthodoxy%20and%20not%20the%20eternal%20values%20%E2%80%93%20as%20it%20is%20sometimes%20made%20out%20to%20be%20by%20appealing%20to%20the%20etymology%20of%20the%20phrase.%20It%20is%20this%20position%20that%20the%20movement%20assumes%20is%20predominant%20than%20the%20meaning.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20John%20Zavos%2C%20a%20scholar%20of%20South%20Asian%20religions%2C%20argues%2C%20this%20idea%20or%20position%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cprominent%20feature%20of%20modern%20Hinduism%20in%20accounts%20of%20political%20and%20social%20history%E2%80%9D.%20That%20position%20was%20one%20of%20traditional%20orthodoxy.%20The%20%3Cem%3EDharma%20Sabha%3C%2Fem%3Es%20of%20the%20nineteenth%20century%20were%20primarily%20instrumental%20in%20creating%20and%20nurturing%20the%20force%20of%20orthodoxy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20orthodoxy%20became%20an%20important%20constituency%2C%20politically%2C%20in%20articulating%20modern%20Hindusim%20of%20the%20orthodox%20kind%20(of%20the%20Dharma%20Sabhas)%20in%20the%20public%20colonial%20space%2C%20as%20against%20the%20reformist%20kind%20of%20modern%20Hinduism%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3ESamajas%3C%2Fem%3E%20(primarily%20the%20Arya%20Samaj%20and%20the%20Brahma%20Samaj).%20Sanatana%20dharma%20thus%20became%20a%20signifier%20of%20orthodoxy%2C%20as%20Zavos%20contends.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20has%20to%20note%20that%20there%20is%20a%20major%20shift%20in%20the%20meaning%20of%20sanatana%20dharma%2C%20from%20the%20one%20laid%20out%20in%20the%20classical%20literature%20to%20the%20one%20that%20finds%20expression%20in%20the%20discourse%20of%2019th-century%20orthodox%20Hinduism.%20In%20this%20discourse%2C%20the%20phrase%20was%20used%20as%20a%20self-description%20of%20one%E2%80%99s%20religious%20tradition.%20In%20this%20self-description%2C%20it%20becomes%20important%20how%20others%20perceive%20this%20tradition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fsanatan-dharma-an-ideology-or-the-entire-hindu-community%5C%22%3ESanatan%20Dharma%3A%20An%20Ideology%20or%20the%20Entire%20Hindu%20Community%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20of%20sanatana%20encapsulates%20the%20idea%20of%20ancientness%2C%20eternality%2C%20permanence%20and%20universalism.%20Dharma%20was%20some%20kind%20of%20law%20that%20holds%20a%20universal%20order%20which%20subsumes%20the%20social%20order.%20In%20their%20mode%20of%20self-representation%20and%20self-description%2C%20these%20characteristics%20were%20drawn%20upon%20only%20to%20project%20the%20idea%20of%20the%20greatness%20of%20this%20religion%20that%20has%20persisted%20over%20a%20long%20period%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESanatana%20dharma%20becomes%20a%20signifier%20of%20a%20position%20of%2C%20as%20Zavos%20terms%20it%2C%20%E2%80%9Camorphous%20homogeneity%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20underlying%20this%20homogeneity%20is%20the%20rigid%20and%20regressive%20orthodoxy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20emerged%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20orthodoxy%20in%20the%20Dharma%20Sabhas%E2%80%99%20articulation%20of%20its%20own%20brand%20of%20Hinduism%2C%20and%20as%20Zavos%20further%20argues%2C%20without%20developing%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdoctrinally%20coherent%20and%20universally%20recognisable%20set%20of%20beliefs%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESuch%20a%20position%20of%20the%20orthodoxy%20of%20the%2019th-century%20focused%20on%20practices%20and%20structures%20which%20clearly%20upheld%20caste%20hierarchy%2C%20the%20subjugation%20of%20women%20and%20all%20other%20regressive%20ideas.%20These%20elements%20came%20together%20to%20stand%20for%20tradition%2C%20and%20the%20Dharma%20Sabhas%20of%2019th-century%20India%20aggressively%20supported%20it%20under%20the%20umbrella%20of%20sanatana%20dharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEradication%20of%20regressive%20orthodoxy%2C%20not%20genocide%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUdhayanidhi%20called%20for%20an%20eradication%20of%20the%20regressive%20orthodoxy%20of%20the%20kind%20that%20prevailed%20in%20the%2019th-century%20%C2%A0%2C%20because%20it%20was%20clearly%20discriminatory.%20Amit%20Malviya%20leaps%20from%20this%20remark%20by%20Udhayanidhi%20on%20sanatana%20dharma%20%E2%80%93%20that%20it%20must%20be%20eradicated%20and%20not%20merely%20opposed%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Famitmalviya%2Fstatus%2F1697951451333763243%5C%22%3Eto%20claim%20that%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9Che%20is%20calling%20for%20genocide%20of%2080%25%20population%20of%20Bharat%2C%20who%20follow%20Sanatan%20Dharma%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGenocide%20is%20a%20word%20coined%20by%20Raphael%20Lemkin%2C%20by%20whose%20indefatigable%20lobbying%20the%20UN%20adopted%20the%20Convention%20on%20the%20Prevention%20and%20Punishment%20of%20the%20Crime%20of%20Genocide%20(1948).%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fen%2Fgenocideprevention%2Fdocuments%2Fatrocity-crimes%2FDoc.1_Convention%2520on%2520the%2520Prevention%2520and%2520Punishment%2520of%2520the%2520Crime%2520of%2520Genocide.pdf%5C%22%3EIn%20its%20definition%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20genocide%20is%20an%20act%20intended%20%E2%80%9Cto%20destroy%2C%20in%20whole%20or%20in%20part%2C%20a%20national%2C%20ethnical%2C%20racial%20or%20religious%20group%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20Malviya%20terms%20Udhayanidhi%E2%80%99s%20calling%20for%20eradication%20as%20genocide%2C%20then%20his%20(Malviya%E2%80%99s)%20understanding%20presupposed%20that%20sanatana%20dharma%20is%20a%20religious%20group%2C%20which%20he%20further%20follows%20up%20by%20saying%20that%2080%25%20of%20the%20population%20of%20Bharat%20are%20followers%20of%20this%20dharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-challenge-to-sanatana-dharma-from-a-radical-politics-of-emancipation%5C%22%3EThe%20Challenge%20to%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20from%20a%20Radical%20Politics%20of%20Emancipation%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20here%20that%20one%20needs%20to%20question%20Malviya%E2%80%99s%20or%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20understanding%20of%20the%20phrase.%20Do%20they%20subscribe%20to%20a%20very%20specific%20meaning%20of%20sanatana%20dharma%2C%20or%20to%20a%20positional%20sense%20of%20the%20orthodoxy%20of%20the%20Dharma%20Sabhas%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20appears%20from%20the%20presupposition%20of%20his%20statement%20that%20it%20is%20the%20latter%2C%20because%20it%20is%20in%20this%20sense%20that%20it%20is%20represented%20as%20a%20constituency%2C%20and%20Malviya%E2%80%99s%20statement%20referring%20to%2080%25%20of%20the%20population%20being%20its%20followers%20also%20clearly%20demarcates%20an%20identifiable%20sense%20of%20religious%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20this%20be%20the%20case%2C%20then%20the%20implication%20is%20clear%20that%20it%20is%20the%20position%20of%20the%20orthodoxy%20of%20the%2019th-century%20Dharma%20Sabhas%E2%80%99%20type%20that%20the%20BJP%20supports%20in%20its%20defence%20of%20sanatana%20dharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20it%20is%20significant%20to%20note%20that%20this%20notion%20of%20Hindu%20orthodoxy%20was%20later%20transformed%20politically%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20V.D.%20Savarkar%20as%20Hindu%20nationalism%20calling%20for%20a%20Hindu%20rashtra.%20So%20when%20Udhayanidhi%20calls%20for%20the%20eradication%20of%20sanatana%20dharma%2C%20it%20is%20not%20only%20the%20regressive%20orthodoxy%2C%20but%20also%20this%20idea%20behind%20the%20politics%20of%20a%20Hindu%20rashtra%20that%20he%20is%20calling%20for%20the%20eradication%20of.%20It%20is%20in%20this%20way%20that%20his%20statement%20has%20to%20be%20viewed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fskamurthi%5C%22%3ES.K.%20Arun%20Murthi%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20taught%20philosophy%20in%20the%20Humanities%20and%20the%20Social%20Sciences%20department%2C%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Science%20Education%20and%20Research%2C%20Mohali%2C%20Punjab.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695656051000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F05134328%2F2020_8img05_Aug_2020_PTI05-08-2020_000062B.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fbjp-defend-orthodox-position-sanatana-dharma-meanings-dont-matter%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20sharp%20exchange%20between%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20and%20the%20BJP%20points%20up%20the%20wide%20gap%20between%20the%20understanding%20of%20the%20pre-19th%20century%20meaning%20of%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20and%20its%2019th-century%20position%20as%20a%20signifier%20of%20orthodoxy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fbjp-defend-orthodox-position-sanatana-dharma-meanings-dont-matter%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistani%20players%20issued%20Indian%20visa%20for%20ICC%20World%20Cup%202023%20travel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695654781000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.busines