gh%20the%20Whatsapp%20groups%2C%20Bheraram%20selects%20regions%20with%20less%20tree%20cover.%20Then%2C%20a%20team%20is%20formed%20to%20work%20on%20the%20ground.%20Soon%20after%2C%20he%20visits%20the%20place%20with%20a%20truckload%20of%20saplings.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPlanting%20a%20sapling%20is%20not%20an%20achievement%20but%20making%20that%20plant%20thrive%20into%20a%20tree%20is.%20Any%20sapling%20needs%20to%20be%20taken%20care%20of%20for%20up%20to%20three%20years.%20As%20an%20individual%2C%20I%20could%20not%20plant%20many%20trees%20with%20a%20regular%20job.%20So%2C%20I%20involved%20communities%20to%20further%20the%20initiative%20at%20a%20large%20scale%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20reach%20out%20to%20local%20people%20and%20motivate%20them%20by%20organising%20%3Cem%3Enukkad%20natak%3C%2Fem%3Es%20(street%20plays).%20Once%20people%20are%20motivated%2C%20convincing%20them%20to%20plant%20saplings%20is%20easier.%20To%20achieve%20this%2C%20first%2C%20we%20evoke%20positive%20emotions%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20ownership%20among%20people%20for%20the%20saplings%20they%20will%20plant.%20We%20ask%20them%20to%20pledge%20to%20protect%20the%20saplings%20until%20they%20become%20trees%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FRajasthan-2-1695644969.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20teacher%20has%20engaged%20at%20least%201.2%20lakh%20citizens%20to%20promote%20the%20concept%20of%20family%20forestry%20and%20letting%20trees%20thrive.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FRajasthan-2-1695644969.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FRajasthan-2-1695644969-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fupl