on%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20role%20demands%20precise%20monitoring%20of%20wildlife%20through%20scientific%20techniques%20and%20the%20careful%20management%20of%20tourism%20through%20the%20creation%20and%20execution%20of%20ecotourism%20initiatives.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDescribing%20her%20work%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirst%20and%20foremost%2C%20I%20need%20to%20be%20an%20effective%20listener%20and%20understand%20how%20this%20famed%20protected%20area%20works.%20I%20have%20a%20great%20team%20with%20one%20of%20the%20finest%20forest%20frontline-to-area%20ratios%20in%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20first%20priority%20would%20be%20to%20continue%20with%20its%20protection%2C%20ensure%20and%20strengthen%20Rhinoceros%20and%20other%20flagship%20species%E2%80%99%20conservation.%20The%20second%20priority%20would%20be%20the%20utmost%20welfare%20of%20the%20forest%20frontline%20staff%20who%20serve%2024%C3%977%20in%20one%20of%20the%20toughest%20conditions%20at%20Kaziranga%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it%20has%20only%20been%2020%20days%20since%20Sonali%20assumed%20the%20new%20responsibility%2C%20she%20is%20quite%20geared%20up%20for%20the%20upcoming%20workload.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20great%20responsibility%20and%20I%20am%20thankful%20to%20the%20state%20government%20for%20giving%20me%20the%20opportunity.%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20wait%20to%20give%20my%20best%20to%20nature%20and%20conserve%20the%20wildlife%20of%20the%20national%20park%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20women%20aspiring%20to%20be%20in%20the%20field%20of%20forest%20and%20wildlife%20conservation%20in%20India%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWomen%20and%20young%20ladies%20who%20love%20outdoors%20and%20want%20to%20make%20a%20difference%2C%20be%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20communities%20must%20drop%20all%20their%20apprehensions%20and%20give%20it%20a%20try.%2