s%20helpless%20when%20they%20found%20out%20about%20the%20girls%E2%80%99%20early%20pregnancies%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-2-1695217326.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Saju%20Vaheed%20brought%20together%20all%20the%20departments%20to%20utilise%20Balika%20Manch%20for%20child%20marriage%20prevention.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-2-1695217326.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-2-1695217326-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-2-1695217326-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-2-1695217326-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-2-1695217326-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330398%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESaju%20Vaheed%20brought%20together%20all%20the%20departments%20to%20utilise%20%3Cem%3EBalika%20Manch%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20child%20marriage%20prevention.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EConsidering%20it%20his%20duty%20as%20DM%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F62502%2Fchild-marriage-education-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprevent%20child%20marriages%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20IAS%20officer%20brought%20together%20all%20the%20departments%20and%20decided%20to%20utilise%20%3Cem%3EBalika%20Manch%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20a%20tool%20for%20child%20marriage%20prevention%20in%20the%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%