0if%20families%20go%20ahead%2C%20we%20send%20police%20officers%20to%20their%20homes%20and%20register%20an%20FIR%20against%20the%20family.%20We%20then%20get%20an%20affidavit%20signed%20by%20the%20parents%20stating%20that%20they%E2%80%99ll%20not%20marry%20off%20their%20daughters%20until%20they%20are%2018%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20collector.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20timely%20intervention%2C%20Saju%20has%20been%20able%20to%20prevent%2090%20planned%20child%20marriages%20in%20the%20district%20in%20the%20past%20year%20with%20the%20help%20of%20158%20school%20clubs%20across%20the%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20work%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20believe%20if%20we%20are%20able%20to%20continue%20this%20way%20for%20another%20year%2C%20we%20will%20be%20able%20to%20eradicate%20child%20marriages%20in%20our%20district.%20Seeing%20the%20progress%20of%20the%20work%2C%20the%20state%20government%20aims%20to%20expand%20this%20initiative%20across%20Tripura.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20work%20is%20deeply%20satisfying%20to%20me%20because%20when%20these%20girls%20talk%20to%20me%2C%20I%20realise%20that%20we%E2%80%99re%20not%20just%20preventing%20marriages%3B%20we%E2%80%99re%20saving%20lives.%20These%20young%20girls%20now%20have%20a%20platform%20to%20voice%20their%20concerns.%20While%20I%E2%80%99m%20involved%20in%20various%20other%20development%20projects%2C%20this%20one%20is%20particularly%20dear%20to%20me.%20I%20believe%20it%20will%20ensure%20a%20better%20future%20for%20generations%20to%20come%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saju.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Saju%20Vaheed.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695218864000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1-1695217206.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D330387%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tripura%20is%20notorious%20for%20child%20mar