20is%20where%20he%20learnt%20about%20their%20biggest%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20drivers%20complained%20of%20one%20single%20problem%20%E2%80%93%20the%20line%20at%20the%20fuel%20station%20was%20very%20long.%20Out%20of%20the%2010%20hours%20they%20spent%20on%20the%20road%2C%20an%20hour%20was%20wasted%20at%20these%20fuel%20stations%20daily.%20The%20cab%20drivers%20told%20me%20that%20they%20lost%2010%20percent%20of%20their%20daily%20earnings%20idling%20away%20in%20the%20queue%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vaibhav%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWouldn%E2%80%99t%20it%20be%20wonderful%20if%20the%20cab%20driver%20could%20know%20which%20fuel%20station%20had%20a%20lesser%20waiting%20time%3F%20And%20that%E2%80%99s%20how%20%E2%80%98Nawgati%E2%80%99%20came%20to%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20of%2020%20then%2C%20and%20in%20his%20third-year%20of%20engineering%2C%20Vaibhav%20thought%20that%20this%20problem%20must%20have%20been%20solved%20by%20someone.%20To%20his%20surprise%2C%20when%20he%20learnt%20that%20there%20was%20no%20solution%2C%20he%20started%20working%20on%20one%20with%20his%20friends%2C%20Aalaap%20Nair%20and%20Aryan%20Sisodia.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20researched%20various%20pain%20points%20from%20the%20perspective%20of%20customers%20and%20fuel%20stations.%20They%20then%20spoke%20to%20fuel%20providers%20and%20examined%20their%20in-house%20challenges%20and%20difficulties.%20After%20this%2C%20they%20built%20the%20technology%2C%20a%20queue%20management%20platform%2C%20which%20would%20help%20both%20fuel%20stations%20and%20customers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHelping%20fuel%20companies%20improve%20efficiency%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-founders2-1695131172.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nawgati%20founders%20Aryan%20Sisodia%2C%20Vaibhav%20Kaushik%20and%20Aalaap%20Nair%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-founders2-1695131172.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-founders2-1695131172-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-founders2-1695131172-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-founders2-1695131172-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-founders2-1695131172-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330322%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENawgati%20founders%20%E2%80%93%20Aryan%20Sisodia%2C%20Vaibhav%20Kaushik%20and%20Aalaap%20Nair.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20came%20up%20with%20two%20solutions%2C%20an%20app%20for%20consumers%2C%20and%20its%20flagship%20product%2C%20Aaveg%2C%20a%20B2B%20platform%2C%20for%20fuel%20companies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20helps%20improve%20compliance%2C%20achieve%20operational%20efficiency%2C%20monitor%20real-time%20congestion%2C%20and%20direct%20customers%20to%20less%20crowded%20stations%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAaveg%20is%20a%20single%20point%20of%20reference%20for%20fuel%20station%20owners%20to%20have%20complete%20oversight%20of%20transit%2C%20waiting%20and%20serving%20time%2C%20attendants%20deployed%2C%20and%20under%20or%20over-utilisation%20of%20resources.%20We%20help%20fuel%20companies%20and%2For%20dealers%20with%20congestion%20management%2C%20compliance%20monitoring%2C%20and%20automating%20forecourt%20operations%2C%20which%20allows%20them%20to%20scale%20up%20or%20scale%20down%20operations%20at%20any%20outlet%20and%20make%20decisions%20backed%20by%20data%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Aryan%2C%20co-founder%20and%20CTO%20at%20Nawgati.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Aaveg%E2%80%99%20which%20is%20Sanskrit%20for%20impulse%2C%20is%20built%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F296093%2Fcouple-converts-tempo-traveller-into-caravan-to-travel-van-life-youtube%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplug-and-play%3C%2Fa%3E%20framework%20and%20aims%20to%20provide%20fuel%20companies%20%E2%80%98data%20within%20an%20impulse%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20vertical%20SaaS%20(software%20as%20a%20service)%20platform%20that%20captures%20real-time%20data%2C%20based%20on%20the%20edge%20devices%20we%20deploy.%20The%20edge%20devices%2C%20in%20simple%20terms%2C%20are%20a%20set%20of%20hardwares%20that%20controls%20data%20flow%20between%20two%20networks%20at%20fuel%20stations.%20Through%20these%20devices%2C%20we%20get%20access%20to%20CCTVs%20and%20dispensers%20at%20the%20stations%2C%20which%20gives%20us%20insights%20into%20the%20congestion%2C%20waiting%20time%2C%20utilisation%20of%20each%20dispenser%2C%20and%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Aryan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20data%20and%20metrics%20help%20companies%20increase%20sales%2C%20reduce%20recurring%20costs%2C%20according%20to%20the%20founders.%20They%20get%20access%20to%20the%20vehicles%20fuelling%20at%20their%20station%2C%20how%20much%20time%20each%20vehicle%20is%20waiting%2C%20how%20much%20time%20is%20spent%20on%20fuelling%20every%20vehicle%2C%20which%20dispensers%20are%20being%20used%20more%2C%20what%20are%20the%20inefficiencies%2C%20amongst%20other%20things.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENawgati%20works%20on%20a%20subscription-based%20model%20and%20charges%20fuel%20stations%20on%20a%20monthly%20basis%2C%20starting%20from%20Rs%205000.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20technology%2C%20that%20is%20saving%20money%20for%20fuel%20companies%2C%20was%20built%20at%20BITS%20Pilani%20in%202019%2C%20through%20the%20college%E2%80%99s%20incubation%20program%2C%20Pilani%20Innovation%20%26amp%3B%20Entrepreneurship%20Development%20Society%20(PIEDS).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20building%20the%20technology%2C%20we%20embarked%20on%20trial%20runs%20that%20led%20us%20to%20a%20pilot%20project%20with%20Indraprastha%20Gas%20Ltd%20(IGL)%20in%202021.%20We%20received%20a%20lot%20of%20valuable%20insights%20regarding%20the%20challenges%20encountered%20by%20the%20teams%20at%20CNG%20stations.%20We%20then%20made%20some%20changes%20to%20enhance%20Aaveg%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Aryan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20pilot%2C%20IGL%20signed%20an%20annual%20contract%20with%20Nawgati.%20Today%2C%20Aaveg%20is%20live%20at%20IGL%2C%20Indian%20Oil%20outlets%20in%20Delhi-NCR%2C%20Mahanagar%20Gas%20(MGL)%20outlets%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20GAIL%20Gas%2C%20Torrent%20Gas%2C%20JioBP%2C%20HP%20Gas%20among%20several%20other%20fuel%20companies%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20plan%20to%20onboard%2015%2C000%20fueling%20outlets%20within%20two%20years.%20The%20startup%20has%20filed%20a%20patent%20for%20this%20technology%2C%20which%20helps%20fuel%20pumps%20manage%20congestion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20Nawgati%20helps%20consumers%2C%20especially%20cab%20drivers%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-app-min-1695131402.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nawgati%20app%20helps%20consumers%20find%20nearest%20fuel%20stations%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-app-min-1695131402.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-app-min-1695131402-170x300.jpg%20170w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-app-min-1695131402-500x883.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-app-min-1695131402-768x1356.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-app-min-1695131402-870x1536.jpg%20870w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-app-min-1695131402-150x265.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330324%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221907%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Nawgati%20app%20helps%20consumers%20find%20the%20nearest%20fuel%20stations.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20solution%20was%20built%20with%20cab%20drivers%20in%20mind%2C%20to%20help%20them%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F304454%2Ftwo-friends-climate-tech-startup-climes-helps-neutralise-carbon-footprint%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esave%20time%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20this%2C%20the%20company%20has%20developed%20an%20application.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNawgati%20fueling%20app%20is%20the%20largest%20fuel%20discovery%20application%20in%20the%20country.%20You%20can%20use%20the%20application%20to%20navigate%20to%20a%20CNG%2Fpetrol%2Fdiesel%20station%20on%20your%20route%2C%20or%20find%20one%20closest%20to%20you.%20We%20have%20more%20than%20a%20million%20downloads%20on%20the%20app%20so%20far%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Vaibhav%2C%20co-founder%20%26amp%3B%20CEO%20of%20Nawgati.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%204-year-old%20app%20is%20currently%20free%2C%20but%20the%20founders%20have%20plans%20to%20roll%20out%20a%20freemium%20model%20soon%2C%20where%20they%20would%20offer%20basic%20features%20for%20free%2C%20but%20charge%20for%20the%20premium%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20founders%20had%20appeared%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20Season%202%20and%20signed%20a%20deal%20of%20Rs%2067%20lakhs%20for%203%20percent%20equity.%20This%20gave%20a%20boost%20to%20Nawgati%20and%20led%20to%20more%20dealers%20reaching%20out%20to%20them.%20The%20startup%20is%20also%20backed%20by%20the%20department%20of%20science%20and%20technology%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20revolutionising%20the%20fuel%20station%20experience%2C%20benefiting%20both%20fuel%20providers%20and%20consumers%20alike.%20Any%20new%20CNG%20station%20is%20now%20listed%20on%20our%20app%20too.%20This%20helps%20fuel%20stations%20get%20more%20sales.%20We%20have%2075000%20fuel%20stations%20listed%20on%20the%20app%20today.%20We%20are%20fuel%20agnostic%2C%20and%20also%20list%20EV%20charging%20stations%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Vaibhav.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERun%20by%20two%2025-year-olds%20and%20one%2024-year-old%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326200%2Fecosoul-home-india-boston-sustainable-plastic-free-kitchenware-cutlery-sugarcane-palm%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20startup%3C%2Fa%3E%20wants%20to%20become%20synonymous%20with%20fuel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20Nawgati%20to%20be%20the%20doctor%20for%20any%20fuel%20related%20problem%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vaibhav.%20Now%2C%20when%20Vaibav%20hops%20onto%20a%20cab%2C%20he%20leads%20the%20driver%20to%20the%20nearest%20fuel%20station%20with%20the%20least%20waiting%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20pictures%20courtesy%3A%20Vaibhav%20Kaushik%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695218288000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-founders2-1695131172.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D330313%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nawgati%2C%20founded%20by%20Vaibhav%20Kaushik%2C%20Aryan%20Sisodia%20and%20Aalaap%20Nair%2C%20wants%20to%20change%20the%20fuel%20station%20experience%20in%20India.%20Its%20B2B%20platform%20'Aaveg'%20offers%20congestion%20monitoring%20thro